</node>
<node id="Service Provider">
  <data key="d0">Service Provider</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Service Provider is an economic operator and commercial entity that offers products or services to consumers as part of their industrial, professional, craft, or commercial activities, whether compensated or not. This term serves as an umbrella concept encompassing merchants and practitioners who offer goods or services electronically, defining the entity whose place of business is being established. Specifically, a Service Provider may refer to an individual practicing a profession subject to specific regulations, which requires a license or permit and obligates the disclosure of certain information.

In terms of transactional and contractual obligations, the Service Provider is responsible for delivering products or services and fulfilling all contractual duties. They are mandated to prepare written price offers prior to providing services, ensuring these documents contain specific details and validity periods. Additionally, the Service Provider must provide consumers with detailed statements regarding contract terms and conditions and issue invoices that clearly detail costs, taxes, and delivery information. When operating electronically, the Service Provider must disclose required data on their electronic location in accordance with Article Six, including their name and distinguishing statements in any electronic declaration.

Regarding quality assurance and legal compliance, the Service Provider bears significant responsibility for managing consumer personal data and electronic communications, adhering strictly to legal restrictions concerning retention periods and permissible usage purposes to uphold privacy rights. If a statutory warranty is breached, the Service Provider is liable for refunding the service value, compensating for deficiencies, or performing the service correctly again. Furthermore, the Service Provider is responsible for creating or publishing electronic advertisements and must adhere to trademark laws. As the primary entity subject to regulatory frameworks, the Service Provider faces potential sanctions for violating specific articles of the relevant Regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;A service provider subject to the regulations, whose electronic premises may be blocked if they violate the System or Regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Service Provider is the entity whose activities and size are considered factors when determining penalties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-757265b902decbf8c55e1b070565644a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc0c7efa3b63af90af17dc69c2eb4ab7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b813a98432e97bd821133a34c3ab82c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef5c3f67882b7588927d8bca42047269&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30e605d9deb7e33ed48fcf51264fb16e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a02c96de615b73a0b4a82ae7b14bc537&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0f30d8785ebf55f768a527b1ede688f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4385a57314892c443871db0108ea1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-17f12893b7ea3153ad9caac0b573a730&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d54b07a7c7ab7c081f38bdd3d484ecc7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7dce39ad69ab952b0a24c9573b89731d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a679e1dd369b0584601fe4f3f1b24454&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0d47d22075e87911525f2b1b1a29585&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db15b26408bc87ab744a17b5b0ea6317&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdd31cd82935851ed60fa97049b2dc09</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814611</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product">
  <data key="d0">Product</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Product is defined broadly as any industrial, agricultural, animal, intellectual, technical, conversion, or digital content item offered to consumers, encompassing both new and used goods, raw materials, and components. Within the Kingdom, tangible products are subject to consumer protection regulations. As the central subject of sales contracts between Economic Operators and Consumers, the Product represents the specific item being sold, advertised, and delivered under agreed terms. It possesses distinct attributes regarding its nature, composition, source, and manufacturing details.

The sale of a Product involves strict regulatory compliance and commercial obligations. Prices must be displayed prominently on the product itself or in advertising. Transactions are governed by rules concerning availability claims, lifecycle management, and return policies. Liability for the loss or damage of the Product depends on delivery status and carrier selection. Crucially, the physical delivery of the Product triggers the cancellation period for the sales contract, marking a key milestone in the consumer’s rights and the completion of the transaction process.&lt;SEP&gt;The Product is the item being sold, which must be returned by the consumer and cared for until return.&lt;SEP&gt;The Product is the item subject to the contract, which must be returned by the Consumer and refunded by the Economic Operator.&lt;SEP&gt;The Product is the tangible item covered by the statutory warranty, subject to repair, replacement, or refund upon breach.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-23f16ba22036bb88da1664b390f68ca1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bea1774b99d54deb70d6648484455df9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfe11211e281ef2abb48c30415b14f61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a056e5bd9daa08695b5a665b53f6d3b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-294b2d78155c5479740e5f6e60fabd5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93b8a69d3470d8fd4caae59080df0a54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814201</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service">
  <data key="d0">Service</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Service is any physical or intellectual activity performed by a service provider for a consumer.&lt;SEP&gt;Intangible offerings provided within the Kingdom, subject to the same regulatory framework as products.&lt;SEP&gt;Services are offerings provided to consumers, subject to the same transparency and fairness requirements as products.&lt;SEP&gt;The intangible offering provided, characterized by its type, location, essential features, and usage warnings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-23f16ba22036bb88da1664b390f68ca1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Establishment">
  <data key="d0">Establishment</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">An Establishment is a specific place, site, or mobile facility where an economic operator regularly conducts business, including websites.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813786</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Address">
  <data key="d0">Address</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">An Address refers to the registered address of an economic operator in the commercial registry, national address, residence, or address on an electronic platform.&lt;SEP&gt;The Address is location data required on an invoice for the Economic Operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Price">
  <data key="d0">Price</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Price is defined as the cost of a product, compensation for a service performance, or consideration for usage.&lt;SEP&gt;The Price of the product or service is a critical financial detail mandated for disclosure.&lt;SEP&gt;The individual price of the product or service listed in the invoice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Defect">
  <data key="d0">Defect</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A Defect is a deficiency in quality, quantity, efficiency, shape, size, or components of a product or service, resulting from errors in design, manufacturing, or presentation, causing harm or deprivation of benefit to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813786</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Advertisement">
  <data key="d0">Advertisement</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Advertisement involves any form of communication aimed at marketing or promoting products or services, or enhancing the reputation of an economic operator in the market.&lt;SEP&gt;Forbidden advertisements must be halted or removed within 24 hours as a corrective measure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c71f72d143d12f0695043e4deb70f183&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Discounts">
  <data key="d0">Discounts</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Discounts involve offering products or services for sale or provision at reduced prices through any method.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813786</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Competition">
  <data key="d0">Competition</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">A Competition is an activity presented directly or via media to consumers under any name, promising the chance of winning financial or material prizes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813786</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Corrective Measures">
  <data key="d0">Corrective Measures</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Corrective Measures are actions taken to prevent violations of the system and regulations, or to correct or eliminate them.&lt;SEP&gt;Corrective measures are actions taken or planned by the economic operator to address identified non-compliance issues.&lt;SEP&gt;Corrective Measures are actions taken in response to identified issues within the market or related to consumers.&lt;SEP&gt;Corrective measures are actions taken to address non-compliance, restricted from being delegated to the private sector.&lt;SEP&gt;Remedial actions that can be taken by the committee against violators as outlined in Article Seventy-Seven.&lt;SEP&gt;Corrective measures are specific actions mandated by the Committee to address violations, including suspending products, stopping advertisements, or restricting platform access.&lt;SEP&gt;Remedial actions mandated under Seventy-Seventh Article, compliance with which is required to avoid penalties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d5f73112067d3017eacad446fe05c6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f17c98aec4af855d06847e8dc54f39d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814439</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Kingdom">
  <data key="d0">Kingdom</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The Kingdom is the geographic jurisdiction within which the competent authority operates and the system applies.&lt;SEP&gt;The Kingdom is the jurisdiction where the contract was offered or executed, determining applicable legal venues.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7a8154749b1feccbfe768628b4e18b60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814017</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Harmful Or Defective Products">
  <data key="d0">Harmful Or Defective Products</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Products or services that are harmful, defective, non-compliant, or unsafe, which the system seeks to protect consumers from.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5921e285b202ad77baf19401a767f275</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813794</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unfair Practices">
  <data key="d0">Unfair Practices</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Practices that infringe upon consumer rights, targeted for elimination by the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5921e285b202ad77baf19401a767f275</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813794</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sustainable Consumption Culture">
  <data key="d0">Sustainable Consumption Culture</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A culture promoting sustainable consumption, encouraged through awareness and education initiatives.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5921e285b202ad77baf19401a767f275</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813794</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Market Surveillance Efficiency">
  <data key="d0">Market Surveillance Efficiency</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The effectiveness of monitoring the market, a goal enhanced by the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5921e285b202ad77baf19401a767f275</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813794</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dispute Resolution">
  <data key="d0">Dispute Resolution</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Mechanisms to facilitate the settlement of disputes arising between consumers and economic operators.&lt;SEP&gt;Dispute resolution is the process facilitated by alternative providers and electronic platforms, governed by Article 70.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5921e285b202ad77baf19401a767f275&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60f77fe5478de7b3d8b2672afe5ee95d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814351</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Stakeholder Participation">
  <data key="d0">Stakeholder Participation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The involvement of consumers and economic operators in providing feedback on relevant systems and regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5921e285b202ad77baf19401a767f275</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813794</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Two">
  <data key="d0">Article Two</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Two is the section of the text that outlines the objectives of the Consumer Protection System.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Two is the specific legal clause that defines the scope of applicability for the system's provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5921e285b202ad77baf19401a767f275&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b912e56726cb9e0d5237d61584a5fa6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814484</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 3 Application Scope">
  <data key="d0">Article 3 Application Scope</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The section defining the scope of application for the system, specifically regarding consumer and economic operator relationships.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23f16ba22036bb88da1664b390f68ca1</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813802</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="The Kingdom">
  <data key="d0">The Kingdom</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The jurisdiction where the products or services are offered and where the consumer resides, governing the application of this system.&lt;SEP&gt;The specific geographical jurisdiction where the system applies and where consumers reside or access services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23f16ba22036bb88da1664b390f68ca1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b912e56726cb9e0d5237d61584a5fa6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814484</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Remote Contract">
  <data key="d0">Remote Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">An agreement concluded between a resident consumer in the Kingdom and an economic operator, deemed to be made at the consumer's residence.&lt;SEP&gt;A Remote Contract refers to an agreement established through distance communication channels, subject to specific termination rights.&lt;SEP&gt;A remote contract is an agreement formed through distance communication channels, subject to specific informational requirements for validity and consumer protection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23f16ba22036bb88da1664b390f68ca1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="E-Commerce">
  <data key="d0">E-Commerce</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A method of trading that does not diminish the level of protection granted to the consumer under this system.&lt;SEP&gt;Electronic commerce is the subject matter governed by Article Twenty-Four, falling under the jurisdiction of the Electronic Transactions Law when not specifically covered by other regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23f16ba22036bb88da1664b390f68ca1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4356d14be0458851058bcbfa4dd8eff9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814638</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Conclusion Location">
  <data key="d0">Contract Conclusion Location</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A legal concept defining that a remote contract with a resident consumer is deemed to be concluded at the consumer's place of residence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23f16ba22036bb88da1664b390f68ca1</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813802</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Four">
  <data key="d0">Article Four</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Four is a legal provision outlining the fundamental rights of consumers within a specific system.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Four is a legal provision regarding electronic communications and consumer rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef5c3f67882b7588927d8bca42047269</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814500</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Rights">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Rights</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer Rights refer to the fundamental protections and entitlements guaranteed to consumers by law, including access to goods, safety, information, and redress.&lt;SEP&gt;Consumer rights include the freedom from coercive conditions, protection against discrimination, and the right to exercise legal entitlements without undue burden.&lt;SEP&gt;Consumer Rights refer to the legal entitlements of consumers regarding repairs, replacements, refunds, and compensation in case of warranty breaches.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814201</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Essential Products And Services">
  <data key="d0">Essential Products And Services</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Essential Products And Services are basic goods and utilities that consumers have the right to access.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813811</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Life Health And Safety">
  <data key="d0">Life Health And Safety</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Life Health And Safety refers to the protection of consumers from risks that threaten their well-being.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813811</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Correct Information">
  <data key="d0">Correct Information</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Correct Information consists of accurate data necessary for consumers to make informed decisions about products or services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813811</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Economic Social And Environmental Impacts">
  <data key="d0">Economic Social And Environmental Impacts</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Economic Social And Environmental Impacts are the consequences of consumer choices that require awareness and education.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813811</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Personal Data Privacy">
  <data key="d0">Personal Data Privacy</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Personal Data Privacy involves safeguarding a consumer's dignity, privacy, and personal information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813811</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Religious Values Public Morals">
  <data key="d0">Religious Values Public Morals</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Religious Values Public Morals are ethical standards that must be respected in the provision of products and services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813811</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dispute Resolution Mechanisms">
  <data key="d0">Dispute Resolution Mechanisms</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Dispute Resolution Mechanisms are effective means for settling consumer conflicts and filing lawsuits when rights are violated.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813812</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Fair Compensation">
  <data key="d0">Fair Compensation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Fair Compensation is the right to receive adequate reparation for damages caused by defective products or services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813812</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Collective Consumer Representation">
  <data key="d0">Collective Consumer Representation</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Collective Consumer Representation refers to the representation of the interests of consumer groups.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813812</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Associations">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Associations</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer Associations are organizations formed by or joined by consumers to advocate for their rights.&lt;SEP&gt;Consumer Associations represent consumer interests and have the standing to initiate legal proceedings to prevent violations.&lt;SEP&gt;Consumer Associations are organizations empowered to file lawsuits on behalf of consumers to claim compensation for damages to their collective rights and interests.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da4dec7a272932b152bbbcd68d8fab88</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814379</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Regulatory Systems And Bylaws">
  <data key="d0">Regulatory Systems And Bylaws</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulatory Systems And Bylaws are legal frameworks related to consumer protection in which consumers can participate and express opinions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813812</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Other Relevant Systems And Regulations">
  <data key="d0">Other Relevant Systems And Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Other Relevant Systems And Regulations refer to additional legal frameworks that may grant consumers further rights beyond those explicitly listed in Article Four.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b09a6ca3331da7c98b328eaa6c42830</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813812</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Five">
  <data key="d0">Article Five</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Five is a legal provision concerning consumer protection, specifically addressing the needs of vulnerable consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19ba78abd7c521789ac7c4a38d25114e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813820</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Relevant Entities">
  <data key="d0">Relevant Entities</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Relevant entities are associated with the competent authority in tasks related to consumer protection laws, regulations, decisions, and procedures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19ba78abd7c521789ac7c4a38d25114e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813820</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vulnerable Consumer">
  <data key="d0">Vulnerable Consumer</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">A Vulnerable Consumer is an individual exposed to greater harm than others due to personal or objective factors affecting their will, perception, decision-making, or choice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19ba78abd7c521789ac7c4a38d25114e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813820</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Protection Regulations">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Protection Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer Protection Regulations encompass systems, laws, regulations, decisions, and procedures aimed at protecting consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19ba78abd7c521789ac7c4a38d25114e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813820</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Age">
  <data key="d0">Age</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Age is a factor that can negatively affect a consumer's will or perception, contributing to their vulnerability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19ba78abd7c521789ac7c4a38d25114e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813820</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Disability">
  <data key="d0">Disability</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Disability is a factor that can negatively affect a consumer's will or perception, contributing to their vulnerability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19ba78abd7c521789ac7c4a38d25114e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813820</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Mental State">
  <data key="d0">Mental State</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Mental state refers to the psychological or mental condition of a consumer, which may impact their decision-making capacity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19ba78abd7c521789ac7c4a38d25114e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813820</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Psychological Condition">
  <data key="d0">Psychological Condition</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Psychological condition is a factor influencing a consumer's ability to make informed choices, potentially leading to vulnerability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-19ba78abd7c521789ac7c4a38d25114e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813820</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Six">
  <data key="d0">Article Six</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Six outlines the mandatory information requirements that economic operators must provide to consumers regarding products or services.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Six is a regulatory provision requiring service providers to disclose specific information on their electronic locations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a02c96de615b73a0b4a82ae7b14bc537</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814513</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Information">
  <data key="d0">Product Information</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Product Information encompasses various attributes such as type, brand, quantity, composition, weight, origin, price, and certifications required by law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Brand Name">
  <data key="d0">Brand Name</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Brand Name is a key identifier for products or services that must be disclosed to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Country Of Origin">
  <data key="d0">Country Of Origin</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Country Of Origin specifies the manufacturing location of the product, which is a mandatory disclosure item.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Manufacturer">
  <data key="d0">Manufacturer</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Manufacturer is the producer of the goods, whose identity and licensing details must be provided if they differ from the seller.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Importer">
  <data key="d0">Importer</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Importer acts on behalf of the manufacturer, and their contact and licensing information must be disclosed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Distributor">
  <data key="d0">Distributor</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Distributor facilitates the supply chain, and their identity must be made available to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Agent">
  <data key="d0">Agent</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Agent represents the manufacturer or distributor, and their details are part of the required transparency measures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Manufacturing Certificate">
  <data key="d0">Manufacturing Certificate</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Manufacturing Certificate is official documentation proving the product meets production standards, required for certain goods.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service License">
  <data key="d0">Service License</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Service License is an authorization document required for the provision of specific regulated services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Regulation">
  <data key="d0">Regulation</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulation constitutes a comprehensive legal framework and legislative instrument that establishes specific administrative rules, obligations, and procedures for economic operators, service providers, and relevant entities. It governs consumer protection and contract law by defining additional informational requirements beyond primary articles, such as Article Six, and outlines procedural steps for executing contract cancellations. The Regulation categorizes contracts exempt from cancellation rights based on product or service nature, specifies conditions for fulfilling warranty breach obligations, grants authority to designate exceptions to statutory warranties, and details rules for using scanning technology for global product numbers. Additionally, it serves as the overarching legal basis under which articles like Article 80 impose duties on various parties.

The Regulation acts as a critical operational guide for technical and maintenance standards, specifying the rules and deadlines for providing spare parts and maintenance services. It provides the necessary tools and procedures to implement quality assurance measures for entities within its scope and defines the required procedures and controls for operating unified networks and alternative dispute resolution mechanisms. Furthermore, it addresses judicial processes by defining specific rules and procedures for lawsuits mentioned in Article Sixty-Three.

In terms of compliance and enforcement, the Regulation defines minor violations, establishes penalty procedures, and sets limits for fines within the system. It also functions as the legal framework or bylaws that define specific requirements regarding independence, transparency, and decision-making effectiveness. By integrating these diverse aspects—from consumer rights and warranty management to technical standards, judicial procedures, and organizational governance—the Regulation ensures a cohesive approach to regulatory oversight and operational integrity across multiple sectors.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulation is the legal document that defines the specific timeframe within which a consumer must report an error.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulation defines other data points that must be disclosed by the Service Provider beyond those explicitly listed in Article Six.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulation defines specific controls and additional data requirements that the service provider must follow based on the nature of each transaction.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulation is the legal framework that defines the specific requirements for the invoice content.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulation is a legal document issued by the Minister based on the System.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bea1774b99d54deb70d6648484455df9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-294b2d78155c5479740e5f6e60fabd5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0931bf17be9284d5fcf4f6332cd19598&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7675218c2feb4f3d03df5d15f853c435&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b54adc716da8570bddd8c2bd41899a6f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d8a453039317884766c4bfb4e705a9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-396aa1e5ed51d610f5f6e15aaf6ec6b6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fe0038af572654f7ea64ab35fd3849a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ef5c3f67882b7588927d8bca42047269&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a02c96de615b73a0b4a82ae7b14bc537&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0f30d8785ebf55f768a527b1ede688f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4385a57314892c443871db0108ea1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3323a5605fc02cf6b08e6daf15866451</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814642</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sequential Number">
  <data key="d0">Sequential Number</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Sequential Number is a specific identifier for the product that must be disclosed as part of the mandatory information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Type">
  <data key="d0">Product Type</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Product Type or group classification is a fundamental attribute required for product identification.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quantity">
  <data key="d0">Quantity</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Quantity of products or services is a mandatory data point to inform the consumer of volume.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813835</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Composition">
  <data key="d0">Composition</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Composition lists the essential components or elements constituting the product or service.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813836</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Weight">
  <data key="d0">Weight</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Weight is a physical attribute of the product that must be disclosed to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813836</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dimensions">
  <data key="d0">Dimensions</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Dimensions (measurement) are physical attributes of the product required for consumer awareness.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813836</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Business Identity Data">
  <data key="d0">Business Identity Data</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Business Identity Data includes trade name, trademark, license data, physical address, phone number, and electronic contact methods.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dbb3cd60b4bd30c2e1383463af5924c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813836</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Seven">
  <data key="d0">Article Seven</data>
  <data key="d1">legalconcept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Seven is a regulation section that outlines the requirements for providing information to consumers.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Seven is a legal provision outlining the obligations of a service provider regarding consumer information disclosure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74786db2b2e6a66a13cddb4bf3ff343b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0f30d8785ebf55f768a527b1ede688f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814522</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumers">
  <data key="d0">Consumers</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumers are the recipients of information provided by advertisers and manufacturers, entitled to clear, accurate, and sufficient data.&lt;SEP&gt;Consumers are one of the parties involved in disputes resolved through alternative means and electronic platforms.&lt;SEP&gt;Consumers are beneficiaries of dispute resolution services, possessing specific rights and obligations towards the service providers.&lt;SEP&gt;Consumers are individuals whose collective rights are protected through lawsuits filed by Consumer Associations, while retaining individual rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74786db2b2e6a66a13cddb4bf3ff343b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60f77fe5478de7b3d8b2672afe5ee95d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da4dec7a272932b152bbbcd68d8fab88</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814379</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Clear Information">
  <data key="d0">Clear Information</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Information intended for consumers must be clear, accurate, adequate, and non-misleading.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74786db2b2e6a66a13cddb4bf3ff343b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Advertising Media">
  <data key="d0">Advertising Media</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Various media including advertisements, labels, stickers, warnings, and usage instructions where consumer information must be displayed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74786db2b2e6a66a13cddb4bf3ff343b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Medium">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Medium</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">An electronic channel allowed for providing information, featuring free printing capabilities.&lt;SEP&gt;Electronic Medium is one of the permissible methods for providing contract terms to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74786db2b2e6a66a13cddb4bf3ff343b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1db2fdbafbec4cf6444dec6b72a0824e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814001</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Usage Instructions">
  <data key="d0">Usage Instructions</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Usage instructions are a specific medium where consumer information must be displayed according to Article Seven.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-74786db2b2e6a66a13cddb4bf3ff343b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813841</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Eight">
  <data key="d0">Article Eight</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Eight is a provision mandating that information provided to consumers must be in Arabic.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Eight is the specific legal provision mandating the issuance of invoices by service providers to consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-979a3a6d1926f5c43b2191f74f9a3804&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4385a57314892c443871db0108ea1b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814533</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Information">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Information</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Information provided to consumers, which is subject to specific language requirements under Article Eight.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-979a3a6d1926f5c43b2191f74f9a3804</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813846</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Arabic Language">
  <data key="d0">Arabic Language</data>
  <data key="d1">language</data>
  <data key="d2">The mandatory primary language for consumer information as specified in Article Eight.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-979a3a6d1926f5c43b2191f74f9a3804</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813846</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Other Languages">
  <data key="d0">Other Languages</data>
  <data key="d1">language</data>
  <data key="d2">Additional languages permitted to be used alongside Arabic for consumer information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-979a3a6d1926f5c43b2191f74f9a3804</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813846</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Providing Methods">
  <data key="d0">Providing Methods</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The various ways, means, or formats through which information is presented to consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-979a3a6d1926f5c43b2191f74f9a3804</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813846</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Nine">
  <data key="d0">Article Nine</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Nine is a regulatory section that mandates the clear declaration of product prices to consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bea1774b99d54deb70d6648484455df9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813851</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Price">
  <data key="d0">Product Price</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Product Price is the specific financial information that must be disclosed to the consumer by the Economic Operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bea1774b99d54deb70d6648484455df9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813851</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Global Product Number">
  <data key="d0">Global Product Number</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Global Product Number is a unique identifier associated with products, linked to scanning technologies defined in regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bea1774b99d54deb70d6648484455df9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813851</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Scanning Technology">
  <data key="d0">Scanning Technology</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Scanning Technology refers to the use of scanners for Global Product Numbers, governed by specific regulatory rules.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bea1774b99d54deb70d6648484455df9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813851</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Ten">
  <data key="d0">Article Ten</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Ten is a legal provision detailing the requirements for service pricing and maintenance information disclosure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-757265b902decbf8c55e1b070565644a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813857</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Price Offer">
  <data key="d0">Price Offer</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Price Offer is a written document containing clear language, provider details, service nature, specific price, and validity period.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-757265b902decbf8c55e1b070565644a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813857</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service And Maintenance Centers">
  <data key="d0">Service And Maintenance Centers</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Service and Maintenance Centers are entities responsible for informing consumers about necessary repair works, durations, and costs, and obtaining explicit consent before proceeding.&lt;SEP&gt;Service And Maintenance Centers are entities obligated to issue invoices for maintenance works and replaced parts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-757265b902decbf8c55e1b070565644a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Maintenance Work">
  <data key="d0">Maintenance Work</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Maintenance work refers to repair activities on products that require notification of duration and cost to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-757265b902decbf8c55e1b070565644a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813858</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service Pricing Disclosure">
  <data key="d0">Service Pricing Disclosure</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The concept of disclosing service pricing, which is the subject of Article Ten.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-757265b902decbf8c55e1b070565644a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813858</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Explicit Consent">
  <data key="d0">Explicit Consent</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Explicit consent from the consumer required before Service and Maintenance Centers perform repair works.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-757265b902decbf8c55e1b070565644a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813858</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Eleven">
  <data key="d0">Article Eleven</data>
  <data key="d1">legalconcept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Eleven is a regulatory clause defining the requirements for comprehensive pricing of products and services.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Eleven is a regulatory provision that prohibits specific deceptive or illegal content in electronic advertisements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-08494eb61cc41dcbd344a3b581092bcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7dce39ad69ab952b0a24c9573b89731d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814549</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Saudi Riyal">
  <data key="d0">Saudi Riyal</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Saudi Riyal is the mandatory currency for stating product or service prices under Article Eleven.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-08494eb61cc41dcbd344a3b581092bcd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813863</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Taxes And Fees">
  <data key="d0">Taxes And Fees</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Taxes and fees are costs that must be included in the comprehensive price of a product or service.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-08494eb61cc41dcbd344a3b581092bcd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813863</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Operating Entity">
  <data key="d0">Operating Entity</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Operating Entity is responsible for disclosing pricing methods when upfront pricing is not feasible.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-08494eb61cc41dcbd344a3b581092bcd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813863</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Or Service">
  <data key="d0">Product Or Service</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Products or services are the items subject to comprehensive pricing regulations, including associated necessary purchases.&lt;SEP&gt;Products or services are the subjects of price reduction activities governed by the regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Product Or Service refers to the goods or offerings provided by the economic operator that must adhere to regulatory standards.&lt;SEP&gt;The subject of the reporting obligation, referring to goods or services provided by the economic operator that may be non-compliant.&lt;SEP&gt;The Product or Service is the subject of the transaction, required to meet warranty requirements and be fit for use at delivery.&lt;SEP&gt;The Product or Service subject to violation may have its provision suspended until the violation is corrected.&lt;SEP&gt;The Product Or Service is the subject of the contract, which the Consumer paid for and can recover if the contract is terminated due to delay.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-08494eb61cc41dcbd344a3b581092bcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6572d1610f6bb7f6ec41fc6f8eb934f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d5f73112067d3017eacad446fe05c6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d15616980ad303389944137db1af4f22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0d47d22075e87911525f2b1b1a29585</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814578</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Necessary Products And Services">
  <data key="d0">Necessary Products And Services</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Products or services that are required to be purchased or used in conjunction with the main product or service.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-08494eb61cc41dcbd344a3b581092bcd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813863</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Twelve">
  <data key="d0">Article Twelve</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Twelve is a legal provision governing price declaration inconsistencies, specifically prohibiting the display of multiple prices for identical goods in a single location.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eba8035888adcd130040e9dbfd9a13d6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813868</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Price Discrepancy">
  <data key="d0">Price Discrepancy</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Price discrepancy refers to the condition where different prices are shown for the same product or service, which is prohibited under Article Twelve unless caused by unintentional error.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eba8035888adcd130040e9dbfd9a13d6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813869</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unintentional Error">
  <data key="d0">Unintentional Error</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Unintentional error is an exception clause that exempts the economic operator from liability if the price difference resulted from a non-deliberate mistake.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eba8035888adcd130040e9dbfd9a13d6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813869</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Products Or Services">
  <data key="d0">Products Or Services</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Products or services refer to the tangible goods or intangible offerings provided by the economic operator, which are subject to single-price display requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-eba8035888adcd130040e9dbfd9a13d6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813869</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Thirteen">
  <data key="d0">Article Thirteen</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Thirteen is a regulatory provision concerning price reductions for products or services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813878</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Reduced Price">
  <data key="d0">Reduced Price</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The reduced price is the new cost of a product or service after a discount is applied.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813878</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Minimum Price History">
  <data key="d0">Minimum Price History</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Minimum Price History refers to the lowest price recorded for a product or service during a specified period.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813878</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Thirty Day Period">
  <data key="d0">Thirty Day Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Thirty Day Period is the mandatory timeframe preceding a price reduction during which minimum prices must be tracked.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813878</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Price Reduction Campaigns">
  <data key="d0">Price Reduction Campaigns</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Price Reduction Campaigns are promotional events explicitly excluded from the strict disclosure requirements of this article.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813878</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Spoilable Products">
  <data key="d0">Spoilable Products</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Spoilable Products are items with short shelf lives subject to specific price reduction rules defined in the subsidiary regulation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813878</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Short-Term Products">
  <data key="d0">Short-Term Products</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Short-Term Products are items with limited usability duration subject to specific price reduction rules defined in the subsidiary regulation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813878</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Subsidiary Regulation">
  <data key="d0">Subsidiary Regulation</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Subsidiary Regulation establishes the specific rules for reducing prices on spoilable and short-term products.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813878</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Regulatory Authority">
  <data key="d0">Regulatory Authority</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Regulatory Authority is the entity empowered to establish subsidiary rules for price reductions.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulatory Authority is the body empowered to determine additional warranty periods for specific products or services based on their nature.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-929aeab810b6ef4b56bb0ac1266d349f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c81dd10f0ce67f495fcaa4afb41ade53</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814184</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Fourteen">
  <data key="d0">Article Fourteen</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Fourteen outlines the regulations regarding the issuance of invoices by economic operators and service centers.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Fourteen is a legal provision detailing consumer rights regarding service delivery delays and contractual termination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0d47d22075e87911525f2b1b1a29585</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814578</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Invoice">
  <data key="d0">Invoice</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">An Invoice is a document, either paper or electronic, detailing transaction data such as identity, price, and date.&lt;SEP&gt;The Invoice is a document provided by the Service Provider to the Consumer after the contract is concluded, listing product costs, total price, fees, taxes, and delivery details.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4385a57314892c443871db0108ea1b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814532</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Commercial Name">
  <data key="d0">Commercial Name</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Commercial Name is specific identification data required on an invoice belonging to the Economic Operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contact Means">
  <data key="d0">Contact Means</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Contact Means include phone numbers or electronic methods for reaching the Economic Operator.&lt;SEP&gt;Contact Means are the communication channels that the Service Provider must disclose on its Electronic Location.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a02c96de615b73a0b4a82ae7b14bc537</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814513</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Description">
  <data key="d0">Product Description</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">A brief description of the product or service purchased, included in the invoice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Date">
  <data key="d0">Contract Date</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The date when the contract or purchase was concluded, recorded in the invoice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Total Payable Price">
  <data key="d0">Total Payable Price</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The comprehensive total amount paid by the consumer, specified in the invoice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Tax Number">
  <data key="d0">Tax Number</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The tax identification number of the Economic Operator, if applicable.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Maintenance Works">
  <data key="d0">Maintenance Works</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Work performed by Service And Maintenance Centers on a product, requiring invoicing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Replaced Parts">
  <data key="d0">Replaced Parts</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Components replaced during maintenance, details of which must be included in the invoice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Proof Methods">
  <data key="d0">Proof Methods</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Various legal ways available to the consumer to prove transaction details if an invoice is not provided.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813889</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Invoice">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Invoice</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">An electronic invoice is a specific format of the invoice that the Economic Operator is obligated to provide alongside or instead of a paper invoice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2d0188b6660d92e46d97b6aa5ddfa898</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813890</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Fifteen">
  <data key="d0">Article Fifteen</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Fifteen is the legal provision titled "Submission of Contract" that mandates the provision of contract copies.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Fifteen is a legal provision regulating the registration of electronic stores in the commercial registry.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9acf77028a44df007ff93e9e4464a66e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0287b0d01cfa4f5a98740f1886983a05</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814585</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Pre-formulated Contract">
  <data key="d0">Pre-formulated Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Pre-formulated Contract is a standard document that must be provided by the Economic Operator to the Consumer at no cost.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9acf77028a44df007ff93e9e4464a66e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813895</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="No Charge">
  <data key="d0">No Charge</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">No Charge refers to the condition that the contract copy must be provided without any financial cost to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9acf77028a44df007ff93e9e4464a66e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813895</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="On Request">
  <data key="d0">On Request</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">On Request indicates that the provision of the contract is triggered by a specific demand from the consumer rather than being automatic.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9acf77028a44df007ff93e9e4464a66e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813895</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Sixteen">
  <data key="d0">Article Sixteen</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Sixteen is a legal provision regarding the burden of proof in consumer information disclosure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c85a7dbe91de94e3f41746b161dffff2</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813902</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Burden Of Proof">
  <data key="d0">Burden Of Proof</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Burden Of Proof refers to the obligation to demonstrate compliance with specific legal or regulatory requirements.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c85a7dbe91de94e3f41746b161dffff2</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813902</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Information Disclosure Obligation">
  <data key="d0">Information Disclosure Obligation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The obligation of the economic operator to provide information to the consumer, which serves as the basis for the burden of proof.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c85a7dbe91de94e3f41746b161dffff2</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813902</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unfair Commercial Practices">
  <data key="d0">Unfair Commercial Practices</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Unfair commercial practices are prohibited behaviors by economic operators that harm consumers, including deceptive advertising, coercion, and data misuse.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813913</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Media Outlet">
  <data key="d0">Media Outlet</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Media outlets are channels used for editorial content promotion, requiring clear labeling of sponsored material when instructed by an economic operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813913</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Personal Data">
  <data key="d0">Personal Data</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Personal data refers to consumer information that must not be collected, stored, or used without explicit consent and prior notification.&lt;SEP&gt;Personal Data refers to information identifying the Consumer, which must be protected and preserved during its retention period by the Service Provider.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-30e605d9deb7e33ed48fcf51264fb16e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814508</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Direct Marketing">
  <data key="d0">Direct Marketing</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Direct marketing involves contacting consumers via phone, electronic means, mail, websites, or apps, which requires a contractual obligation or explicit consent.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813913</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Payment Method">
  <data key="d0">Payment Method</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Payment methods are instruments used for transactions, where fees charged to consumers cannot exceed the costs incurred by the economic operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813913</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unjustified Conditions">
  <data key="d0">Unjustified Conditions</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Conditions that are burdensome or unjustified, which economic operators are prohibited from imposing on consumers exercising their rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813913</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Discrimination">
  <data key="d0">Discrimination</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Unjustified differentiation between consumers based on race, gender, or nationality, which is explicitly prohibited.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813913</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Deceptive Advertising">
  <data key="d0">Deceptive Advertising</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Advertising practices that claim limited availability without sufficient stock or use misleading editorial content, which are banned.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813913</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Lifecycle Manipulation">
  <data key="d0">Product Lifecycle Manipulation</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The act of shortening a product's lifecycle or reducing its efficiency to increase consumption without justification, which is prohibited.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-811c2282e5faf0e8745c51115a8604e5</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813913</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Misleading Commercial Practices">
  <data key="d0">Misleading Commercial Practices</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Commercial practices involving false information, concealment of relevant data, or presentation methods that deceive consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Eighteen">
  <data key="d0">Article Eighteen</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The specific legal article establishing prohibitions against misleading commercial practices.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Eighteen is a regulatory provision outlining penalties for violations of the system or regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Eighteen defines the specific penalties that the Committee is authorized to impose.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5661f438c3dca334dc944b7a2eeeb87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdd31cd82935851ed60fa97049b2dc09</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814611</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Awards">
  <data key="d0">Awards</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Honors received by the product or service, which must not be misrepresented.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Certifications">
  <data key="d0">Certifications</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Official confirmations of quality or compliance received by the product or service, which must not be misrepresented.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quality Marks">
  <data key="d0">Quality Marks</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Symbols indicating quality standards for the product or service, which must not be misrepresented.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trademarks">
  <data key="d0">Trademarks</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Distinctive signs used to identify the product or service, which must not be misrepresented.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Logos">
  <data key="d0">Logos</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Visual symbols associated with the product or service, which must not be misrepresented.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="False Discounts">
  <data key="d0">False Discounts</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Claims of price reductions that are not factual, constituting a misleading practice.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Warranty">
  <data key="d0">Warranty</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6fb2c83cde8c36de94f7057d58fb2869</data>
  <data key="d2">The warranty and after-sales services associated with a service are elements that must not be misrepresented.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813927</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Nineteen">
  <data key="d0">Article Nineteen</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Nineteen is a regulatory provision governing comparative advertising, outlining specific requirements for comparisons between products or services.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Nineteen of the System, specifically Paragraph 1, which establishes the Committee responsible for handling referred violations.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Nineteen establishes the framework for a committee to investigate violations of regulations and impose penalties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a9356ec391f6d77e79bbb8d92e8e7958&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db15b26408bc87ab744a17b5b0ea6317&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdd31cd82935851ed60fa97049b2dc09</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814610</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Comparative Advertising">
  <data key="d0">Comparative Advertising</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Comparative advertising refers to advertisements that explicitly or implicitly compare a product or service with those of another economic operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a9356ec391f6d77e79bbb8d92e8e7958</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813933</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Needs">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Needs</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer needs represent the requirements satisfied by the products or services being compared, which must be identical for the comparison to be valid.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a9356ec391f6d77e79bbb8d92e8e7958</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813933</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Key Advantages">
  <data key="d0">Key Advantages</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Key advantages refer to one or more main features of a product or service that can be used for comparison and must be verifiable.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a9356ec391f6d77e79bbb8d92e8e7958</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813933</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Competitor Reputation">
  <data key="d0">Competitor Reputation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Competitor reputation refers to the public standing of a rival business, which must not be misrepresented or distorted in comparative advertising.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a9356ec391f6d77e79bbb8d92e8e7958</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813933</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Misleading Practice">
  <data key="d0">Misleading Practice</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A misleading practice is a deceptive action or claim in advertising that is explicitly prohibited under Article Nineteen.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a9356ec391f6d77e79bbb8d92e8e7958</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813933</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 20 Electronic Advertising">
  <data key="d0">Article 20 Electronic Advertising</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 20 establishes the legal framework and requirements for sending electronic advertisements to consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c71f72d143d12f0695043e4deb70f183</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813942</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Email Address">
  <data key="d0">Email Address</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Email Address is the specific communication channel used to send advertisements, requiring explicit consent from the owner.&lt;SEP&gt;An Email Address associated with a specific country does not create a presumption that the Service Provider's place of business is in that country.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c71f72d143d12f0695043e4deb70f183&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b813a98432e97bd821133a34c3ab82c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814494</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Prior Explicit Consent">
  <data key="d0">Prior Explicit Consent</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Prior Explicit Consent is a mandatory condition that must be obtained from the consumer before sending any advertising email.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c71f72d143d12f0695043e4deb70f183</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813942</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Advertising Content Requirements">
  <data key="d0">Advertising Content Requirements</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A set of rules mandating that ads clearly identify themselves as advertising, disclose the sender's identity, and provide an opt-out mechanism.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c71f72d143d12f0695043e4deb70f183</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813942</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sender Identity Disclosure">
  <data key="d0">Sender Identity Disclosure</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The requirement for the advertisement to clearly state the identity of the economic operator publishing it on their behalf.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c71f72d143d12f0695043e4deb70f183</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813942</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Opt-Out Mechanism">
  <data key="d0">Opt-Out Mechanism</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The method provided to consumers to stop receiving future electronic advertisements sent via electronic means.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c71f72d143d12f0695043e4deb70f183</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813942</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Implementing Regulations">
  <data key="d0">Implementing Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Implementing Regulations are the legal provisions necessary to execute and enforce the rules set out in Article 20 on Electronic Advertising.&lt;SEP&gt;The Implementing Regulations define the criteria for identifying extraordinary price increases and specify the temporary procedures to be applied.&lt;SEP&gt;Implementing Regulations specify the technical and procedural requirements for providing information in remote contracts, including those concluded via electronic platforms.&lt;SEP&gt;Implementing Regulations define the methods for confirming consumer consent and specify the conditions and procedures for modifying orders.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c71f72d143d12f0695043e4deb70f183&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20c777b39e1e4bbef77c2e5719e36820&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbcbc9c6d4024ed107a3aed8073f87c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814132</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Twenty-One">
  <data key="d0">Article Twenty-One</data>
  <data key="d1">legaldocument</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Twenty-One is a regulatory provision concerning advertising content directed at children, prohibiting harmful messages and age-inappropriate products.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Twenty-One is a legal provision that stipulates the conditions and methods for publishing the operative part of a penalty decision.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a0621a29a827530e6d64c79f4cced1de&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85d489500ac41fa5ad12a8c9462979b4</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814626</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Children Advertising">
  <data key="d0">Children Advertising</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Children advertising refers to marketing messages specifically targeted at a young demographic, subject to strict safety and appropriateness regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a0621a29a827530e6d64c79f4cced1de</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813946</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Child Safety">
  <data key="d0">Child Safety</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Child safety represents the well-being of children, which is protected from serious harm by prohibitions in advertising content.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a0621a29a827530e6d64c79f4cced1de</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813946</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Age-Inappropriate Products">
  <data key="d0">Age-Inappropriate Products</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Age-inappropriate products are goods or services that do not align with the developmental stages or ages of the target child audience.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a0621a29a827530e6d64c79f4cced1de</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813946</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Protection Law Article 22">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Protection Law Article 22</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 22 of the Consumer Protection Law regulates communication charges between consumers and economic operators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec82bc886475d035ec952d60da6a6e6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813952</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Approved Communication Tariff">
  <data key="d0">Approved Communication Tariff</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The approved communication tariff is the standard rate set for telephone communications, which serves as the maximum limit for charges.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec82bc886475d035ec952d60da6a6e6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813952</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Communication Means">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Communication Means</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Electronic communication means include digital channels provided by economic operators for interacting with consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec82bc886475d035ec952d60da6a6e6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813953</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Artificial Intelligence">
  <data key="d0">Artificial Intelligence</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Artificial intelligence is mentioned as a technology used in direct or indirect communication with consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec82bc886475d035ec952d60da6a6e6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813953</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Websites">
  <data key="d0">Websites</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Websites are online platforms provided by economic operators for communicating with consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec82bc886475d035ec952d60da6a6e6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813953</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Telephone Communications">
  <data key="d0">Telephone Communications</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Telephone communications are voice-based interactions between the consumer and the economic operator, subject to fee caps based on approved tariffs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec82bc886475d035ec952d60da6a6e6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813953</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 23: Reductions">
  <data key="d0">Article 23: Reductions</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 23 of the Regulations addresses the rules and conditions regarding reductions, prohibiting misleading practices and outlining regulatory oversight.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56229fb9380fc83bd53da4c959da6c7c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813959</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Misleading Practices">
  <data key="d0">Misleading Practices</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Practices that deceive consumers or participants, which are explicitly prohibited during reduction campaigns under the Regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56229fb9380fc83bd53da4c959da6c7c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813959</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="The Regulations">
  <data key="d0">The Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The overarching legal framework containing Article 23 and associated Bylaws that govern commercial activities such as reductions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56229fb9380fc83bd53da4c959da6c7c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813960</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Bylaws">
  <data key="d0">Bylaws</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulatory documents that define the specific terms, conditions, and controls for announcing and conducting reduction campaigns.&lt;SEP&gt;Bylaws provide specific controls and guidelines for delegating market surveillance activities to the private sector.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56229fb9380fc83bd53da4c959da6c7c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Reduction Campaigns">
  <data key="d0">Reduction Campaigns</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Campaigns involving the announcement and execution of price reductions, subject to regulatory conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-56229fb9380fc83bd53da4c959da6c7c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813960</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="The Fourteenth Article">
  <data key="d0">The Fourteenth Article</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Fourteenth Article is a legal provision concerning competitions, outlining licensing requirements and operational rules.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a6516eb7274d47a5878b05ae794d1f0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813966</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Competitions">
  <data key="d0">Competitions</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Competitions are events regulated by The Fourteenth Article, requiring licenses and specific disclosure details for organization.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a6516eb7274d47a5878b05ae794d1f0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813966</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Competition License">
  <data key="d0">Competition License</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Competition License is an official permit required to hold or advertise competitions, issued by the Competent Authority.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a6516eb7274d47a5878b05ae794d1f0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813966</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Competition Coupon">
  <data key="d0">Competition Coupon</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Competition Coupons are documents used for participation in competitions, subject to restrictions on placement within products.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a6516eb7274d47a5878b05ae794d1f0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813966</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Competition Details">
  <data key="d0">Competition Details</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Competition Details refer to the specific information required in an application, including name, purpose, geographic scope, duration, results announcement date, prize delivery deadline, participation conditions, prizes, and coupon samples.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a6516eb7274d47a5878b05ae794d1f0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813966</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Prizes">
  <data key="d0">Prizes</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Prizes are rewards distributed to winners, which must be documented as being in the possession of the Economic Operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a6516eb7274d47a5878b05ae794d1f0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813966</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Or Service Purchase Requirement">
  <data key="d0">Product Or Service Purchase Requirement</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">This is a prohibited practice where participation in a competition is conditioned on buying a product or service.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9a6516eb7274d47a5878b05ae794d1f0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813967</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Twenty-Five">
  <data key="d0">Article Twenty-Five</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Twenty-Five is a legal provision regarding the concealment or withholding of strategic products and services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2228f5a1f65a7fcad0b31452f9941e5d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813972</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Strategic Products And Services">
  <data key="d0">Strategic Products And Services</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Strategic products and services are items designated by authority for special regulation regarding their availability and trade.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2228f5a1f65a7fcad0b31452f9941e5d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813972</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Head Of The Competent Authority">
  <data key="d0">Head Of The Competent Authority</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Head Of The Competent Authority is the official responsible for issuing decisions that define strategic products and services.&lt;SEP&gt;The Head of the Competent Authority is the individual authorized to issue appointments for inspectors and establish rules for financial rewards.&lt;SEP&gt;The Head of the Competent Authority is the official responsible for issuing the regulation specified in Article Eighty-One.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2228f5a1f65a7fcad0b31452f9941e5d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53d255606873f798c277f71c669581e4</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814451</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Holders Of Strategic Products">
  <data key="d0">Holders Of Strategic Products</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Holders Of Strategic Products are individuals or entities possessing strategic items for non-personal use who are obligated to report to authorities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2228f5a1f65a7fcad0b31452f9941e5d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813972</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Trade">
  <data key="d0">Trade</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Trade refers to the act of buying and selling strategic products or services, which is restricted by the concealment prohibition.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2228f5a1f65a7fcad0b31452f9941e5d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813972</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Personal Use">
  <data key="d0">Personal Use</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Personal use is the criterion used to exempt certain holders from the reporting obligation regarding strategic products.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-2228f5a1f65a7fcad0b31452f9941e5d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813972</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 26">
  <data key="d0">Article 26</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 26 is a legal provision that grants authority to take temporary measures against extraordinary price increases during emergencies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-20c777b39e1e4bbef77c2e5719e36820</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813978</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Extraordinary Price Increases">
  <data key="d0">Extraordinary Price Increases</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Extraordinary Price Increases are sudden, significant rises in prices occurring under exceptional circumstances, which the article aims to regulate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-20c777b39e1e4bbef77c2e5719e36820</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813978</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Competent Authority President">
  <data key="d0">Competent Authority President</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Competent Authority President is the official empowered to implement temporary measures to control price hikes after receiving approval.&lt;SEP&gt;The head of the competent authority who has the power to establish the Review Committee, issue its working rules, and determine member allowances.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-20c777b39e1e4bbef77c2e5719e36820&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Emergency Circumstances">
  <data key="d0">Emergency Circumstances</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Emergency Circumstances refer to crises, pandemics, and other exceptional situations that trigger the conditions for price regulation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-20c777b39e1e4bbef77c2e5719e36820</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813978</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cabinet Council">
  <data key="d0">Cabinet Council</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Cabinet Council is the governing body whose approval is required before the Competent Authority President can enforce temporary measures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-20c777b39e1e4bbef77c2e5719e36820</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813978</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Interests">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Interests</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer Interests represent the protected rights and economic well-being of consumers from the impact of excessive pricing.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-20c777b39e1e4bbef77c2e5719e36820</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813978</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Temporary Measures">
  <data key="d0">Temporary Measures</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Temporary Measures are the specific actions taken by the Competent Authority President to limit extraordinary price increases, as defined in Article 26.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-20c777b39e1e4bbef77c2e5719e36820</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813978</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Twenty-Seven">
  <data key="d0">Article Twenty-Seven</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Twenty-Seven outlines the conditions and applicability of contracts, specifically distinguishing between standard and negotiated forms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb13f1b3abd5cc99dd565ac09795ffc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813983</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Contracts">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Contracts</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Contracts concluded with consumers, which are subject to the regulations defined in Article Twenty-Seven.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb13f1b3abd5cc99dd565ac09795ffc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813983</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Standard Contract">
  <data key="d0">Standard Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A pre-drafted contract form prepared by the economic operator, serving as a baseline against which negotiated terms are compared.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb13f1b3abd5cc99dd565ac09795ffc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813983</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Negotiated Contract">
  <data key="d0">Negotiated Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A contract where terms have been individually discussed, which takes precedence over standard contract terms under the regulation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb13f1b3abd5cc99dd565ac09795ffc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813983</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Burden of Proof">
  <data key="d0">Burden of Proof</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The legal obligation placed on the economic operator to demonstrate that specific contract terms were subject to negotiation.&lt;SEP&gt;The Burden of Proof is the legal obligation placed on the consumer to demonstrate that they have exercised their right to cancel the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;The legal obligation placed on the economic operator to prove compliance with the notification requirements set forth in Article 38.&lt;SEP&gt;The Burden of Proof refers to the legal obligation placed on the consumer to demonstrate that they have terminated the contract.&lt;SEP&gt;The Burden of Proof rests on the Economic Operator to demonstrate compliance with the requirement to provide necessary information to the Consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fb13f1b3abd5cc99dd565ac09795ffc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-294b2d78155c5479740e5f6e60fabd5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ee11e2f2efdecd0a6233d3dde78ac94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Information Disclosure">
  <data key="d0">Contract Information Disclosure</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A regulatory requirement mandating that the Economic Operator provide specific details such as descriptions, identity, contact info, price, payment terms, return policies, and risk warnings before concluding a contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Used Product Sale Regulations">
  <data key="d0">Used Product Sale Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Specific rules requiring the disclosure of defects in used products and the provision of technical reports for used vehicles by licensed maintenance providers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Vehicle Maintenance Service Provider">
  <data key="d0">Vehicle Maintenance Service Provider</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A licensed entity authorized to perform vehicle maintenance and issue official technical reports on the condition and defects of used vehicles.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Technical Report">
  <data key="d0">Technical Report</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">An official document issued by a licensed maintenance provider detailing the condition and defects of a used vehicle, required during the sale of such vehicles.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dispute Resolution Platforms">
  <data key="d0">Dispute Resolution Platforms</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Alternative means or electronic platforms designated for resolving consumer disputes outside of traditional litigation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813994</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product or Service Description">
  <data key="d0">Product or Service Description</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Basic descriptions and characteristics of the product or service that must be provided to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813995</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Economic Operator Identity Data">
  <data key="d0">Economic Operator Identity Data</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Identity details of the economic operator, including commercial name and address.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813995</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contact Information">
  <data key="d0">Contact Information</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Contact details for the economic operator, such as phone number and email address.&lt;SEP&gt;Includes postal and electronic addresses required to be made available to the public.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8eba08bab139116de9ee95fe214a7f7e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814366</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Payment and Delivery Terms">
  <data key="d0">Payment and Delivery Terms</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Terms regarding payment, delivery, shipping, and execution if contract performance is deferred.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813995</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Return and Exchange Policy">
  <data key="d0">Return and Exchange Policy</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Policies governing the replacement and return of products or services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813995</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Installation and Maintenance Conditions">
  <data key="d0">Installation and Maintenance Conditions</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Conditions for the installation, use, and maintenance of the product, where applicable.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813995</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Duration and Termination">
  <data key="d0">Contract Duration and Termination</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The duration of the contract or conditions for its termination if it is indefinite or automatically renewable.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813995</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Usage Risks and Prevention">
  <data key="d0">Usage Risks and Prevention</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Risks associated with using the product or service, along with methods to prevent, mitigate, or eliminate them.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813995</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Complaint Handling Procedure">
  <data key="d0">Complaint Handling Procedure</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Policies and procedures for handling consumer complaints, including dedicated email addresses.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-05ecf93d1d9a52151af2a72301234ed7</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776813995</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 29">
  <data key="d0">Article 29</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 29 is a legal provision regarding the supply of contract terms to consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1db2fdbafbec4cf6444dec6b72a0824e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814000</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Terms">
  <data key="d0">Contract Terms</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Contract Terms are the conditions that must be supplied to the consumer in a clear, understandable, accurate, and non-misleading manner.&lt;SEP&gt;Contract Terms refer to the conditions and clauses within an agreement, where ambiguities are addressed by Article 34.&lt;SEP&gt;The terms and conditions agreed upon between the Economic Operator and the Consumer, serving as a benchmark for product conformity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1db2fdbafbec4cf6444dec6b72a0824e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d152ef32e10dd0dd90a99794e2ce09a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814161</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Oral Communication">
  <data key="d0">Oral Communication</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Oral Communication is one of the permissible methods for providing contract terms to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1db2fdbafbec4cf6444dec6b72a0824e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814000</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Written Document">
  <data key="d0">Written Document</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Written Document is one of the permissible methods for providing contract terms to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1db2fdbafbec4cf6444dec6b72a0824e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814000</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 30">
  <data key="d0">Article 30</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 30 is a legal provision prohibiting unfair terms in contracts between economic operators and consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10fae82f7c6a76b4dbf01080c7ed22eb</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814006</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unfair Terms">
  <data key="d0">Unfair Terms</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Unfair terms are contractual conditions that create a significant imbalance in rights and obligations, to the detriment of the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10fae82f7c6a76b4dbf01080c7ed22eb</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814006</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract">
  <data key="d0">Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Contract is a legal agreement that serves as the foundational basis for transactions between an Economic Operator (or Service Provider) and a Consumer. This relationship can be established electronically, particularly within the context of electronic commerce. The scope of the Contract encompasses the regulation of various operational aspects, including the sale, delivery, and performance of products or services. It also explicitly governs potential cancellations and defines the rights associated with such actions, specifically referencing Article 13 regarding cancellation rights. Furthermore, the formation and validity of the Contract are subject to specific regulatory frameworks, notably Article 31.

From a legal standpoint, the Contract triggers specific obligations, such as the duty of the Service Provider to issue an invoice to the Consumer. Its terms remain valid even if certain individual clauses are deemed void due to being unfair, ensuring the continuity of the legal relationship. Additionally, the Contract plays a crucial role in determining jurisdictional factors, such as the place of business, especially when parties maintain multiple locations. By defining these parameters, the Contract clarifies the rights, duties, and procedural rules binding the Economic Operator and the Consumer throughout the duration of their commercial interaction.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10fae82f7c6a76b4dbf01080c7ed22eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dfe11211e281ef2abb48c30415b14f61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc0c7efa3b63af90af17dc69c2eb4ab7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b813a98432e97bd821133a34c3ab82c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed4385a57314892c443871db0108ea1b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98520f83d72a9bac06aacc6991d7d823&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0d47d22075e87911525f2b1b1a29585</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814580</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contractual Rights">
  <data key="d0">Contractual Rights</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Contractual Rights refer to the entitlements of the parties within the agreement, which must not be significantly imbalanced.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10fae82f7c6a76b4dbf01080c7ed22eb</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814007</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contractual Obligations">
  <data key="d0">Contractual Obligations</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Contractual Obligations refer to the duties of the parties within the agreement, which must not be significantly imbalanced.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-10fae82f7c6a76b4dbf01080c7ed22eb</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814007</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 31">
  <data key="d0">Article 31</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 31 defines prohibited conditions in contracts between the Economic Operator and the Consumer as inherently prejudicial.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814017</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Regulations">
  <data key="d0">Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulations refer to the statutory rules and by-laws that define the obligations of the Economic Operator.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulations are specific rules implementing the System, which economic operators must follow.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulations define the standards and conditions required to establish the habitual residence as the place of business for certain practitioners.&lt;SEP&gt;Legal rules that may define additional exceptions to the consumer's right of withdrawal based on the nature of products or services.&lt;SEP&gt;The Regulations define the necessary controls and requirements for registering electronic premises as stipulated by Article Fifteen.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7b813a98432e97bd821133a34c3ab82c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98520f83d72a9bac06aacc6991d7d823&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0287b0d01cfa4f5a98740f1886983a05</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814585</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Judicial System">
  <data key="d0">Judicial System</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Judicial System represents the courts and legal proceedings available to the Consumer for dispute resolution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814017</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Other Country Law">
  <data key="d0">Other Country Law</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Other Country Law refers to the legal systems of foreign nations that cannot be imposed on disputes arising within the Kingdom.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814017</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Liability Exemption">
  <data key="d0">Liability Exemption</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Liability Exemption refers to the prohibited condition where the Economic Operator is exempted from responsibility for fault or negligence.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814017</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unilateral Modification Right">
  <data key="d0">Unilateral Modification Right</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Unilateral Modification Right refers to the prohibited condition granting the Economic Operator the power to cancel, modify, or interpret contract terms unilaterally for their benefit.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814017</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dispute Resolution Clause">
  <data key="d0">Dispute Resolution Clause</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Dispute Resolution Clause refers to conditions prohibiting or limiting the Consumer's right to access courts or forcing litigation in a foreign court.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6e82925b2fc83bb4036c3b1f007ba923</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814017</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Delivery Period">
  <data key="d0">Delivery Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Delivery Period is a maximum duration of fifteen days from the date of contract conclusion, during which the Economic Operator must deliver the product unless otherwise agreed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dfe11211e281ef2abb48c30415b14f61</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814027</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Refund Period">
  <data key="d0">Refund Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Refund Period is a maximum duration of fourteen days from the date of notification of contract termination, within which the Economic Operator must return the consumer's payment.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dfe11211e281ef2abb48c30415b14f61</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814027</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Thirty-Two">
  <data key="d0">Article Thirty-Two</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Thirty-Two is the specific legal provision titled "Product Delivery" that outlines the obligations and rights regarding the delivery of products.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dfe11211e281ef2abb48c30415b14f61</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814027</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Delay Notification">
  <data key="d0">Delay Notification</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Delay Notification refers to the requirement for the Economic Operator to inform the Consumer of any expected delays or difficulties affecting delivery or contract execution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dfe11211e281ef2abb48c30415b14f61</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814027</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Conclusion Date">
  <data key="d0">Contract Conclusion Date</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Contract Conclusion Date is the reference point from which the fifteen-day delivery period begins to calculate.&lt;SEP&gt;The Contract Conclusion Date marks the beginning of the seven-day termination period for service-based contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dfe11211e281ef2abb48c30415b14f61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814099</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Cancellation Notification Date">
  <data key="d0">Cancellation Notification Date</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dfe11211e281ef2abb48c30415b14f61</data>
  <data key="d2">The Refund Period is calculated starting from the date the Consumer notifies the termination of the contract.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814028</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Thirty-Three: Liability for Loss">
  <data key="d0">Article Thirty-Three: Liability for Loss</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Thirty-Three, titled "Liability for Loss," outlines the legal responsibilities regarding the loss or destruction of products in sales contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4a056e5bd9daa08695b5a665b53f6d3b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814034</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Carrier">
  <data key="d0">Carrier</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The carrier is an entity designated to transport the product, whose appointment affects the allocation of liability between the consumer and the operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4a056e5bd9daa08695b5a665b53f6d3b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814034</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Delivery">
  <data key="d0">Delivery</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Delivery is the critical event that transfers liability for the Product from the Economic Operator to the Consumer, unless specific exceptions apply.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4a056e5bd9daa08695b5a665b53f6d3b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814034</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 34">
  <data key="d0">Article 34</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 34 is a legal provision concerning the interpretation of contract terms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5d152ef32e10dd0dd90a99794e2ce09a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814038</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Clause">
  <data key="d0">Clause</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Clause refers to a specific provision or section within the Contract Terms that may contain ambiguities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5d152ef32e10dd0dd90a99794e2ce09a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814038</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Thirty-Five">
  <data key="d0">Article Thirty-Five</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Thirty-Five is a legal provision governing contracts signed outside the economic operator's business premises.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23ea8c91412652822b5737482cd0f932</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814047</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Outside Business Premises">
  <data key="d0">Contract Outside Business Premises</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A contract for selling products or providing services that is concluded outside the economic operator's location under specific conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23ea8c91412652822b5737482cd0f932</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814047</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sale Of Product Or Service Provision">
  <data key="d0">Sale Of Product Or Service Provision</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The commercial activity involving selling goods or offering services, which is subject to the regulations in Article Thirty-Five.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23ea8c91412652822b5737482cd0f932</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814047</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Visit Outside Premises">
  <data key="d0">Visit Outside Premises</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">An occasion where the economic operator meets the consumer away from their own business location.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23ea8c91412652822b5737482cd0f932</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814047</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Residence">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Residence</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The home of the consumer, where a visit by the economic operator can trigger the conditions of this article.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23ea8c91412652822b5737482cd0f932</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814047</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Workplace">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Workplace</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The place of work of the consumer, where a visit by the economic operator can trigger the conditions of this article.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-23ea8c91412652822b5737482cd0f932</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814047</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 36">
  <data key="d0">Article 36</data>
  <data key="d1">legaldocument</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 36, titled "Right to Cancel the Contract," is a legal provision governing consumer rights regarding contract cancellation.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 36 contains the specific period during which the consumer may exercise the right to terminate the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-294b2d78155c5479740e5f6e60fabd5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ee11e2f2efdecd0a6233d3dde78ac94</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814074</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Seven-Day Period">
  <data key="d0">Seven-Day Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Seven-Day Period is the timeframe within which a consumer may exercise their right to cancel a contract without providing reasons or incurring costs.&lt;SEP&gt;The Seven-Day Period is the statutory timeframe during which a consumer may terminate a remote contract without providing reasons or incurring costs.&lt;SEP&gt;The Seven-Day Period is the maximum duration allowed for the Consumer to return the product after notifying the Economic Operator.&lt;SEP&gt;The Seven-Day Period is the time frame during which a consumer may exercise the right to withdraw from a contract without penalty, provided no benefit has been derived.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-294b2d78155c5479740e5f6e60fabd5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98520f83d72a9bac06aacc6991d7d823</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814570</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Cancellation">
  <data key="d0">Contract Cancellation</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Contract Cancellation is the legal act of terminating an agreement, resulting in the discharge of obligations for both parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-294b2d78155c5479740e5f6e60fabd5b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814054</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 42">
  <data key="d0">Article 42</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 42 is a referenced legal provision that lists specific types of contracts exempt from the consumer's right of cancellation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-294b2d78155c5479740e5f6e60fabd5b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814054</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Subcontract">
  <data key="d0">Subcontract</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Subcontract is a secondary agreement arising from the main contract that is also terminated upon cancellation.&lt;SEP&gt;Subcontracts are secondary agreements arising from the main remote contract that are extinguished upon its termination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-294b2d78155c5479740e5f6e60fabd5b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814099</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 37">
  <data key="d0">Article 37</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 37 outlines the obligations of parties when a contract is terminated, specifically regarding product returns and refund processes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-93b8a69d3470d8fd4caae59080df0a54</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814067</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Termination">
  <data key="d0">Contract Termination</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Contract Termination is the event that triggers the obligations for the consumer to return the product and the operator to refund the money.&lt;SEP&gt;Contract Termination is the event triggering the obligations for the Consumer to return the product and the Economic Operator to issue a refund.&lt;SEP&gt;Contract Termination is a specific remedy available to the consumer, allowing them to end the contract as a response to harm caused by the economic operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-93b8a69d3470d8fd4caae59080df0a54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e2e9d4353bb95f7bca809f541cd54320</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814300</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Seven-Day Return Period">
  <data key="d0">Seven-Day Return Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Seven-Day Return Period is the maximum duration allowed for the consumer to return the product after notifying the economic operator of termination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-93b8a69d3470d8fd4caae59080df0a54</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814067</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Fourteen-Day Refund Period">
  <data key="d0">Fourteen-Day Refund Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Fourteen-Day Refund Period is the maximum duration allowed for the economic operator to refund all amounts received from the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-93b8a69d3470d8fd4caae59080df0a54</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814067</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Systematic Warranty">
  <data key="d0">Systematic Warranty</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Systematic Warranty refers to the legal guarantee mentioned in Article 49, limiting the consumer's use of the product to verification purposes only.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-93b8a69d3470d8fd4caae59080df0a54</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814067</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 49">
  <data key="d0">Article 49</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 49 defines the systematic warranty provisions under which the consumer's usage of the product is limited.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 49 refers to the statutory warranty provisions that define the necessary usage limits for verifying agreement with the guarantee during the return period.&lt;SEP&gt;Article 49 is the specific regulation referenced regarding the disclosure of warranty defects.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-93b8a69d3470d8fd4caae59080df0a54&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d15616980ad303389944137db1af4f22</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814191</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 38">
  <data key="d0">Article 38</data>
  <data key="d1">legaldocument</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 38 is a legal provision concerning the notification of the consumer's right to terminate a contract and its terms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9ee11e2f2efdecd0a6233d3dde78ac94</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814074</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Termination Right">
  <data key="d0">Contract Termination Right</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The right to terminate a contract without cause or cost, as stipulated in Article 38.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9ee11e2f2efdecd0a6233d3dde78ac94</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814074</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Mediator">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Mediator</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">An electronic mediator is a channel through which the economic operator can provide clear and understandable information to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9ee11e2f2efdecd0a6233d3dde78ac94</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814074</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 28">
  <data key="d0">Article 28</data>
  <data key="d1">legaldocument</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 28 is a referenced legal provision that modifies or complements the obligations stated in Article 38.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-9ee11e2f2efdecd0a6233d3dde78ac94</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814074</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Thirty-Nine">
  <data key="d0">Article Thirty-Nine</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Thirty-Nine is a legal provision establishing regulations for contracts concluded remotely.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Remote Sales Contract">
  <data key="d0">Remote Sales Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A Remote Sales Contract is defined as an agreement between an economic operator and a consumer, including the sale of products or services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Sale">
  <data key="d0">Product Sale</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The sale of products constitutes one of the activities covered by remote contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service Provision">
  <data key="d0">Service Provision</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The provision of services constitutes another activity covered by remote contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Communication Media">
  <data key="d0">Communication Media</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Communication media refer to the tools used to conclude remote contracts, such as telephone, fax, mail, and websites.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Telephone">
  <data key="d0">Telephone</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Telephone is identified as a medium for concluding remote contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Fax">
  <data key="d0">Fax</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Fax is identified as a medium for concluding remote contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Mail">
  <data key="d0">Mail</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Mail is identified as a medium for concluding remote contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Website">
  <data key="d0">Website</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Websites are identified as mediums for concluding remote contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814082</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="System Regulations">
  <data key="d0">System Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">System Regulations provide the overarching legal framework granting protection to consumers in remote transactions.&lt;SEP&gt;System regulations refer to the overarching legal framework governing the conduct of market surveillance.&lt;SEP&gt;The System Regulations are the legal framework whose application generates disputes and compensation claims addressed in Article 22.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c47f120917e5636d314c4a5e75774c7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-505a7da5372dbf86a3bdc9b55579249e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814629</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Forty">
  <data key="d0">Article Forty</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Forty is a legal provision that outlines exceptions to the application of rules regarding off-premises contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0931bf17be9284d5fcf4f6332cd19598</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814091</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Off-Premises Contracts">
  <data key="d0">Off-Premises Contracts</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Off-Premises Contracts refer to agreements made away from business premises, which are generally subject to specific protective regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0931bf17be9284d5fcf4f6332cd19598</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814091</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Automatic Vending Machines">
  <data key="d0">Automatic Vending Machines</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Automatic Vending Machines are devices used to sell goods or services, serving as an exception where off-premises contract rules do not apply.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0931bf17be9284d5fcf4f6332cd19598</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814091</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Financial Service Contracts">
  <data key="d0">Financial Service Contracts</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Financial Service Contracts are agreements related to financial services, explicitly excluded from the scope of off-premises contract regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0931bf17be9284d5fcf4f6332cd19598</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814091</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Remote Contracts">
  <data key="d0">Remote Contracts</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Remote Contracts, also referred to as off-premises contracts, are agreements made through distance communication channels, subject to specific regulatory exceptions under Article Forty.&lt;SEP&gt;Remote Contracts are agreements concluded at a distance, which generate specific legal disputes under Article Seventy-Four.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0931bf17be9284d5fcf4f6332cd19598&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ec93773600936293052d86178a78f903</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814385</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 41">
  <data key="d0">Article 41</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 41 is a legal provision governing the right of consumers to terminate contracts concluded remotely.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814098</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Delivery Date">
  <data key="d0">Product Delivery Date</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The Product Delivery Date marks the beginning of the seven-day termination period for goods-based contracts.&lt;SEP&gt;The date on which the product was received by the consumer, serving as one of the start points for the withdrawal period.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98520f83d72a9bac06aacc6991d7d823</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814570</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Termination Regulation">
  <data key="d0">Termination Regulation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Termination Regulation is the regulatory framework that specifies the procedural requirements for executing contract termination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814099</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Authorized Representative">
  <data key="d0">Authorized Representative</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">An Authorized Representative is a person other than the carrier designated by the Consumer to receive the product, triggering the start of the withdrawal period.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814099</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Termination of Remote Contract">
  <data key="d0">Termination of Remote Contract</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-301a4ffbdfd6fdb0a956239d0553872e</data>
  <data key="d2">Upon termination of the Remote Contract by the Consumer, any associated Subcontracts are extinguished.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814099</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Right To Cancel Contract">
  <data key="d0">Right To Cancel Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Right To Cancel Contract is a consumer protection mechanism that allows consumers to void certain agreements, subject to specific exceptions and conditions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service Contracts">
  <data key="d0">Service Contracts</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Service Contracts are agreements for services where execution has been completed or requires explicit consent regarding waiver of cancellation rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814106</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Digital Content">
  <data key="d0">Digital Content</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Digital Content refers to digital materials provided via electronic intermediaries or custom-designed products, which may restrict cancellation rights upon execution.&lt;SEP&gt;Digital Content refers to digital material supplied to consumers under a sales contract, subject to specific warranty duration rules.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c81dd10f0ce67f495fcaa4afb41ade53</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814184</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Periodical Publications">
  <data key="d0">Periodical Publications</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Periodical Publications include newspapers, magazines, and newsletters, which are generally exempt from the consumer's right to cancel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Software Programs">
  <data key="d0">Software Programs</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Software Programs refer to closed computer programs or audio/video recordings that have been opened after delivery, affecting cancellation eligibility.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Accommodation And Transport Services">
  <data key="d0">Accommodation And Transport Services</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Accommodation And Transport Services involve housing, logistics, car rentals, catering, and passenger transport scheduled for specific dates or durations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Defective Products">
  <data key="d0">Defective Products</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Defective Products are items that do not meet specified standards, explicitly excluded from restrictions on cancellation rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Improper Use">
  <data key="d0">Improper Use</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Improper Use refers to consumer actions leading to product defects, which disqualify the consumer from exercising the right to cancel.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Forty-Two">
  <data key="d0">Article Forty-Two</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Forty-Two is the specific legal provision establishing exceptions to the consumer's right to cancel a contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bc991839dd0cc98acaf12ea5bc58ecc8</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814107</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 43">
  <data key="d0">Article 43</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 43 outlines the obligations of parties when a contract is terminated, specifically concerning consumer rights and business responsibilities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814117</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Fourteen-Day Period">
  <data key="d0">Fourteen-Day Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Fourteen-Day Period is the maximum duration allowed for the Economic Operator to refund all amounts received from the Consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814117</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Refund Amounts">
  <data key="d0">Refund Amounts</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Refund Amounts refer to all monetary sums received by the Economic Operator from the Consumer, which must be returned upon contract termination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814117</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Refund Method">
  <data key="d0">Refund Method</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2</data>
  <data key="d2">The Economic Operator must refund using the same method used by the Consumer unless otherwise agreed or technically impossible, without charging fees.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814118</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Statutory Warranty">
  <data key="d0">Statutory Warranty</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-019c5b0704e7195269616af2f7e331e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d15616980ad303389944137db1af4f22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bbdc0bdfb37532b71f5f2a12cb9f8fe0</data>
  <data key="d2">The Statutory Warranty referenced in Article 49 provides the legal framework for verifying the product's condition during the return period.&lt;SEP&gt;The Statutory Warranty is a legal guarantee whose provisions are explicitly limited by Article 48 regarding certain exclusions.&lt;SEP&gt;Statutory Warranty is a legal guarantee ensuring products or services are free from defects and conform to specific standards and agreements.&lt;SEP&gt;Statutory Warranty is the legal guarantee protecting the consumer, the breach of which is defined in this article.&lt;SEP&gt;Statutory Warranty is the legal guarantee provided for products and services, the breach of which triggers specific consumer protections.&lt;SEP&gt;The Statutory Warranty is the mandatory legal guarantee protecting consumer rights, which remains unaffected and unpaid by any additional warranty.</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814208</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Forty-Four">
  <data key="d0">Article Forty-Four</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Forty-Four is a legal provision detailing the mandatory information that economic operators must provide to consumers prior to concluding remote contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Identity Data">
  <data key="d0">Identity Data</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Identity Data includes the business name and address of the Economic Operator, which must be disclosed clearly to the Consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Direct Communication Means">
  <data key="d0">Direct Communication Means</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Direct Communication Means refer to the effective contact methods provided by the Economic Operator to facilitate interaction with the Consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Right of Withdrawal">
  <data key="d0">Right of Withdrawal</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Right of Withdrawal allows the Consumer to cancel the contract without providing reasons or incurring costs within a specified period, governed by Article Forty-One.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Payment Methods Information">
  <data key="d0">Payment Methods Information</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Payment Methods Information comprises detailed data regarding how payments are to be made for the goods or services involved in the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Obligation to Inform">
  <data key="d0">Obligation to Inform</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Obligation to Inform is the legal duty placed on the Economic Operator to disclose all relevant details, including payment commitments, to ensure the Consumer's informed consent.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Platforms">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Platforms</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Electronic Platforms are digital interfaces through which remote contracts may be concluded, requiring adherence to specific informational standards defined by regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Electronic Platforms are digital tools or systems facilitating the resolution of disputes between consumers and economic operators.&lt;SEP&gt;Electronic Platforms are digital intermediaries that facilitate mediation between service providers and consumers, falling under regulatory oversight.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b54adc716da8570bddd8c2bd41899a6f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b93d95a5b6df178db9b2bb6cde162f61</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814589</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Forty-One">
  <data key="d0">Article Forty-One</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Forty-One establishes the timeframe during which the Consumer's right of withdrawal is valid for exercising cancellation without penalty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Formation Commitment">
  <data key="d0">Contract Formation Commitment</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The obligation to inform the Consumer that entering into the contract entails a payment commitment, which is a prerequisite for the contract to be binding on the Consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a4d1807f1fc70cd86f3926044c5b150a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814127</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Forty-Five">
  <data key="d0">Article Forty-Five</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Forty-Five establishes the consumer's right to modify their remote order, outlining specific timeframes and conditions for such modifications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bbcbc9c6d4024ed107a3aed8073f87c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814132</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Remote Contract Agreement">
  <data key="d0">Remote Contract Agreement</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Remote Contract Agreement is the transaction initiated by the consumer, which triggers the rights and obligations outlined in Article Forty-Five.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bbcbc9c6d4024ed107a3aed8073f87c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814132</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Twenty-Four Hour Period">
  <data key="d0">Twenty-Four Hour Period</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Twenty-Four Hour Period is the standard timeframe during which a consumer may modify their order after consent, unless otherwise agreed or fulfilled.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bbcbc9c6d4024ed107a3aed8073f87c9</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814132</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Forty-Six">
  <data key="d0">Article Forty-Six</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Forty-Six is a legal provision concerning product or service compliance with standards and specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Forty-Six defines the specific requirements against which product or service compliance is measured.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c6572d1610f6bb7f6ec41fc6f8eb934f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d5f73112067d3017eacad446fe05c6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Standards And Specifications">
  <data key="d0">Standards And Specifications</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Standards And Specifications encompass standard requirements, quality criteria, and other conditions mandated for compliance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c6572d1610f6bb7f6ec41fc6f8eb934f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814137</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quality Standards">
  <data key="d0">Quality Standards</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Quality Standards are criteria defined within Article Forty-Six that the Economic Operator must ensure products or services meet.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c6572d1610f6bb7f6ec41fc6f8eb934f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814137</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Forty-Seven">
  <data key="d0">Article Forty-Seven</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Forty-Seven is a legal provision establishing reporting obligations regarding non-compliant products or services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d5f73112067d3017eacad446fe05c6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Or Service Non-Compliance">
  <data key="d0">Product Or Service Non-Compliance</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Non-compliance refers to products or services that materially fail to meet specified requirements, including defects and potential harm.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d5f73112067d3017eacad446fe05c6c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814143</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ten Days">
  <data key="d0">Ten Days</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A ten-day period during which the economic operator must report non-compliance after discovery or knowledge of the issue.&lt;SEP&gt;The maximum time period, in days, within which the Committee must make a decision regarding a referred violation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6d5f73112067d3017eacad446fe05c6c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db15b26408bc87ab744a17b5b0ea6317</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814597</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 48">
  <data key="d0">Article 48</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 48 outlines exceptions to the statutory warranty, specifying which contracts and products are excluded from its provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814152</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Digital Content Contracts">
  <data key="d0">Digital Content Contracts</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Contracts for providing digital content or digital services are generally excluded from the statutory warranty unless integrated with products.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814152</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Digital Services">
  <data key="d0">Digital Services</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Digital services are provided under contracts that are typically excluded from the statutory warranty unless linked to physical products.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814153</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Third Party">
  <data key="d0">Third Party</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A Third Party can provide digital content or services bundled with products, influencing the scope of the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814153</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Compulsory Execution Products">
  <data key="d0">Compulsory Execution Products</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Products sold through compulsory execution are excluded from the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814153</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Specialized Authority">
  <data key="d0">Specialized Authority</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A Specialized Authority conducts sales through which certain products are excluded from the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814153</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Used Products">
  <data key="d0">Used Products</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Used products sold via public auction are specifically excluded from the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814153</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Public Auction">
  <data key="d0">Public Auction</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Public Auction is the method of sale through which used products lose their eligibility for the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814153</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Live Animals">
  <data key="d0">Live Animals</data>
  <data key="d1">creature</data>
  <data key="d2">Live animals are explicitly listed as products excluded from the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814153</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Statutory Warranty Chapter">
  <data key="d0">Statutory Warranty Chapter</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The chapter containing statutory warranty provisions, whose articles define the scope and exceptions of the warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5086b6cf9bc02c27ea5fb4cb9ed609ed</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814153</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Digital Product Updates">
  <data key="d0">Digital Product Updates</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Updates for digital products, including necessary security updates, which must be provided by the Economic Operator to maintain warranty compliance.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814161</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sample Or Model">
  <data key="d0">Sample Or Model</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">A physical sample or model presented to the consumer before the contract is signed, against which the delivered product must match.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814161</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Specifications">
  <data key="d0">Product Specifications</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The defined specifications, installation instructions, and usage guidelines for the product or service as stated in the contract.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814161</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Advertising And Labels">
  <data key="d0">Advertising And Labels</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Information issued by the Economic Operator through advertisements, labels, or identification cards that informs consumers about product features.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814161</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Last Consumer Owner">
  <data key="d0">Last Consumer Owner</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The final individual who owns the product, to whom the Statutory Warranty remains valid even after ownership transfer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814162</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Forty-Nine">
  <data key="d0">Article Forty-Nine</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Forty-Nine is the specific legal provision detailing the Statutory Warranty regulations for economic operators and consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814162</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Regulatory Regulation">
  <data key="d0">Regulatory Regulation</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Regulatory Regulation defines the type of information that must be clarified to the consumer and the method of notification regarding the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-70049c2c9beee67be467a0bc1e8e5319</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814162</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 50">
  <data key="d0">Article 50</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 50 is a legal provision titled "Error in Assembly" that defines conditions under which assembly errors constitute a warranty breach.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5b3ef01cc61802e9c5898cf34fea5a1c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814175</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Assembly Error">
  <data key="d0">Product Assembly Error</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A defect or fault occurring during the assembly or installation of a product, potentially leading to warranty liability.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5b3ef01cc61802e9c5898cf34fea5a1c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814175</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Warranty Breach">
  <data key="d0">Warranty Breach</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A violation of the warranty terms, established in this context by specific types of assembly errors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5b3ef01cc61802e9c5898cf34fea5a1c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814175</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sales Contract">
  <data key="d0">Sales Contract</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The agreement between parties that may explicitly assign responsibility for product assembly and installation to the economic operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5b3ef01cc61802e9c5898cf34fea5a1c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814176</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Assembly Instructions">
  <data key="d0">Assembly Instructions</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Guidelines provided by the economic operator for installing the product; errors in these instructions can shift liability to the operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5b3ef01cc61802e9c5898cf34fea5a1c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814176</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Economic Operator's Supervision">
  <data key="d0">Economic Operator's Supervision</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The oversight provided by the economic operator during the assembly or installation of the product, which establishes their liability for errors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5b3ef01cc61802e9c5898cf34fea5a1c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814176</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Warranty">
  <data key="d0">Product Warranty</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Product Warranty refers to the guarantee provided by the Economic Operator regarding the quality and functionality of physical goods.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c81dd10f0ce67f495fcaa4afb41ade53</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814184</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service Warranty">
  <data key="d0">Service Warranty</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Service Warranty refers to the guarantee provided by the Economic Operator regarding the performance of services rendered.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c81dd10f0ce67f495fcaa4afb41ade53</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814184</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Digital Service">
  <data key="d0">Digital Service</data>
  <data key="d1">service</data>
  <data key="d2">Digital Service refers to digital services supplied to consumers under a sales contract, subject to specific warranty duration rules.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c81dd10f0ce67f495fcaa4afb41ade53</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814184</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Two-Year Period">
  <data key="d0">Two-Year Period</data>
  <data key="d1">duration</data>
  <data key="d2">A standard two-year period applicable to product warranties and digital content/services provided over short durations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c81dd10f0ce67f495fcaa4afb41ade53</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814184</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="One-Year Period">
  <data key="d0">One-Year Period</data>
  <data key="d1">duration</data>
  <data key="d2">A minimum one-year period applicable to warranties on used goods and general service warranties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c81dd10f0ce67f495fcaa4afb41ade53</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814184</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 51">
  <data key="d0">Article 51</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 51 is the specific legal provision governing the standard warranty duration for economic operators in this text.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c81dd10f0ce67f495fcaa4afb41ade53</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814184</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 52">
  <data key="d0">Article 52</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 52 specifies the conditions under which there is no breach of statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d15616980ad303389944137db1af4f22</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814191</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Conclusion">
  <data key="d0">Contract Conclusion</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Contract Conclusion is the event where the agreement between the Economic Operator and Consumer is finalized.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d15616980ad303389944137db1af4f22</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814191</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Misuse">
  <data key="d0">Misuse</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Misuse refers to improper handling by the Consumer, which exempts the Economic Operator from warranty liability if proven.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d15616980ad303389944137db1af4f22</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814191</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 53">
  <data key="d0">Article 53</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 53 outlines the rights of consumers when there is a breach of the statutory warranty, detailing obligations for economic operators and service providers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814201</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Compensation">
  <data key="d0">Compensation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Compensation is the remedy available to the consumer for damages arising from a breach of the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814201</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Damages">
  <data key="d0">Damages</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Damages are the harms or losses suffered by the consumer that result from the breach of the statutory warranty.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4f2ea9e729aab0deda37682e004b3fc6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814201</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Additional Warranty">
  <data key="d0">Additional Warranty</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An Additional Warranty is a voluntary guarantee provided by the Economic Operator, distinct from the statutory warranty, which must be clearly identified and documented separately.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bbdc0bdfb37532b71f5f2a12cb9f8fe0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814208</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Warranty Document">
  <data key="d0">Warranty Document</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Warranty Document is an independent written record or electronic medium detailing the terms of the Additional Warranty, including scope, duration, cost, and exceptions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bbdc0bdfb37532b71f5f2a12cb9f8fe0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814208</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Intermediary">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Intermediary</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">An Electronic Intermediary is a channel or platform through which an Economic Operator can present an Additional Warranty to a Consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-bbdc0bdfb37532b71f5f2a12cb9f8fe0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814208</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 55">
  <data key="d0">Article 55</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 55 is the specific legal article establishing obligations regarding spare parts and maintenance services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7675218c2feb4f3d03df5d15f853c435</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814214</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Spare Parts And Maintenance Services">
  <data key="d0">Spare Parts And Maintenance Services</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Spare Parts and Maintenance Services are the goods and services that must be provided by the economic operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7675218c2feb4f3d03df5d15f853c435</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814214</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Duration Of Availability">
  <data key="d0">Duration Of Availability</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Duration of Availability is the specific time period determined by the nature of the product or service, during which spare parts and maintenance must be supplied.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-7675218c2feb4f3d03df5d15f853c435</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814214</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 56">
  <data key="d0">Article 56</data>
  <data key="d1">legaldocument</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 56 is a legal provision mandating economic operators to inform consumers about the duration required to provide spare parts upon contracting.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0bb91dbf0d0d74be15a1f23f7ef09d39</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814218</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Spare Parts">
  <data key="d0">Spare Parts</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Spare parts are components that must be provided by the Economic Operator, with their supply timeline disclosed to the Consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0bb91dbf0d0d74be15a1f23f7ef09d39</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814218</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Fifty-Seven">
  <data key="d0">Article Fifty-Seven</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Fifty-Seven is a regulatory provision concerning market surveillance procedures to ensure compliance with laws and protect consumers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5dc591f6a06f37fe2f1b3209ca356c15</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Economic Operators">
  <data key="d0">Economic Operators</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Economic Operators are business entities subject to market surveillance and required to comply with system regulations and ordinances.&lt;SEP&gt;Economic operators are the other party in disputes with consumers, engaging in processes overseen by the competent authority.&lt;SEP&gt;Economic operators engage with dispute resolution platforms, holding defined rights and obligations alongside consumers.&lt;SEP&gt;Economic Operators are entities obligated under Article 80 to reconcile their situations in accordance with the regulation's provisions within a specified timeframe.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5dc591f6a06f37fe2f1b3209ca356c15&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60f77fe5478de7b3d8b2672afe5ee95d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4fe0038af572654f7ea64ab35fd3849a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814444</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Protection Rules">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Protection Rules</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer Protection Rules refer to the standards, guidelines, and procedures established by the competent authority to safeguard consumer interests.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5dc591f6a06f37fe2f1b3209ca356c15</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814227</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="System And Regulations">
  <data key="d0">System And Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The System and Regulations are the legal framework governing economic operators, which compliance is verified by the competent authority.&lt;SEP&gt;The System And Regulations refer to the legal framework and rules that Consumers Associations enforce through lawsuits against violators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5dc591f6a06f37fe2f1b3209ca356c15&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-da4dec7a272932b152bbbcd68d8fab88</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814379</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Market Surveillance">
  <data key="d0">Market Surveillance</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Market Surveillance is the process conducted by the competent authority to monitor the market and ensure adherence to regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Market Surveillance involves the observation and monitoring of market practices and consumer behaviors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5dc591f6a06f37fe2f1b3209ca356c15&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 58">
  <data key="d0">Article 58</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 58 is a regulatory provision titled "Surveillance Tools" that mandates the adoption of appropriate systems for consumer protection.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Relevant Authorities">
  <data key="d0">Relevant Authorities</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Relevant Authorities and concerned parties are entities responsible for implementing surveillance systems and monitoring consumer-related data.&lt;SEP&gt;Relevant Authorities are external bodies that inspectors may consult or utilize when necessary to perform their duties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Surveillance Systems">
  <data key="d0">Surveillance Systems</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Surveillance Systems refer to the appropriate database and information exchange mechanisms required for monitoring facts, complaints, and behaviors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Protection">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Protection</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer Protection is the domain in which market surveillance and corrective measures are applied to ensure safety and rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Penalties">
  <data key="d0">Penalties</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Penalties are sanctions imposed in the context of consumer protection enforcement.&lt;SEP&gt;Penalties are punitive actions enforced by the Competent Authority, not delegable to the private sector.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f17c98aec4af855d06847e8dc54f39d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdd31cd82935851ed60fa97049b2dc09</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Database Systems">
  <data key="d0">Database Systems</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Database Systems are specific technical systems required for the collection and exchange of monitored information.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Information Exchange">
  <data key="d0">Information Exchange</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Information Exchange is the process of sharing monitored data between relevant parties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Facts">
  <data key="d0">Facts</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Facts refer to the objective occurrences related to consumers that are monitored.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Complaints">
  <data key="d0">Complaints</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Complaints are reports from consumers or other sources regarding issues, which are monitored and recorded.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Behaviors">
  <data key="d0">Behaviors</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Behaviors refer to the actions of consumers that are subject to monitoring.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Market Monitoring Procedures">
  <data key="d0">Market Monitoring Procedures</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Market Monitoring Procedures are the specific steps taken to oversee market activities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8d3fef46affeb71273796cdeced53169</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814235</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Inspectors">
  <data key="d0">Inspectors</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Inspectors are officials appointed by the competent authority to perform monitoring, inspection, investigation, and evidence collection duties, holding criminal police status.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814247</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Fifty-Nine">
  <data key="d0">Article Fifty-Nine</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Fifty-Nine is the legal provision defining the appointment, duties, powers, and obligations of inspectors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814247</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Inspection Powers">
  <data key="d0">Inspection Powers</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Inspection Powers refer to the specific authorities granted to inspectors, including entry, document retrieval, sampling, and undercover purchases.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814247</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Criminal Police Status">
  <data key="d0">Criminal Police Status</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Criminal Police Status is the official designation granting inspectors the authority to conduct investigations and secure evidence in a manner similar to law enforcement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Confidentiality Principles">
  <data key="d0">Confidentiality Principles</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Confidentiality Principles are the mandatory standards inspectors must uphold to protect professional, commercial, and personal data privacy.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Financial Rewards">
  <data key="d0">Financial Rewards</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Financial Rewards are monetary incentives established by the competent authority for inspectors who successfully uncover system or regulation violations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Workplaces And Premises">
  <data key="d0">Workplaces And Premises</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Workplaces and Premises include shops, offices, branches, warehouses, storage areas, and vehicles used by the economic operator, which inspectors may enter and inspect.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Documents And Data">
  <data key="d0">Documents And Data</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Documents, information, data, and records related to violations are subject to retrieval, examination, seizure, and retention by inspectors.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Surveillance Recordings">
  <data key="d0">Surveillance Recordings</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Surveillance recordings from shop cameras are accessible to inspectors as evidence for verifying compliance with regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Products And Services">
  <data key="d0">Products And Services</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Products and services are the subjects of inspection, testing, and sampling to verify adherence to system provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="System And Regulation">
  <data key="d0">System And Regulation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The System and Regulation refers to the legal framework and rules whose violations are monitored and enforced by the inspectors.&lt;SEP&gt;The System and Regulation define the legal framework, including Article Seventeen and Article Nineteen, governing service providers and regulatory actions in Saudi Arabia.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db15b26408bc87ab744a17b5b0ea6317</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814596</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Representative Of Economic Operator">
  <data key="d0">Representative Of Economic Operator</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Representative of the Economic Operator is a person working for the operator who may be summoned by inspectors for questioning.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Other Persons">
  <data key="d0">Other Persons</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Other Persons include anyone with relevant information or witnesses that inspectors can summon to assist in uncovering violations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e1c5c3874985bccf0474e63d7c12c51d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814248</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Sixty">
  <data key="d0">Article Sixty</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Sixty is the regulatory section governing the procedures for inspection reports and inspector conduct.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Inspection Report">
  <data key="d0">Inspection Report</data>
  <data key="d1">document</data>
  <data key="d2">The Inspection Report is a formal document prepared by an inspector after completing an inspection, containing specific mandatory details.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Inspector">
  <data key="d0">Inspector</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Inspector is the authorized individual responsible for conducting inspections and preparing the associated report.&lt;SEP&gt;The Inspector is the authority responsible for identifying minor violations and imposing administrative penalties on economic operators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814266</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Person At Location">
  <data key="d0">Person At Location</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Persons present at the economic operator's location, whose names, IDs, and titles must be recorded in the report.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Supporting Documents">
  <data key="d0">Supporting Documents</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Documents attached to the inspection report deemed necessary by the inspector to clarify and evaluate facts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Inspection Activities">
  <data key="d0">Inspection Activities</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The activities performed by inspectors during an inspection, which cannot be hindered or obstructed by anyone.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Inspection Results">
  <data key="d0">Inspection Results</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The outcomes and findings derived from the inspection activities, which must be included in the report.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Facts Of Inspection">
  <data key="d0">Facts Of Inspection</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The specific details and occurrences of the inspection that are recorded to provide a factual basis for the report.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Statements">
  <data key="d0">Statements</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Information or declarations obtained from any person present at the inspection site, attached as part of the record.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="False Information">
  <data key="d0">False Information</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Incorrect or misleading data provided by persons, which is explicitly prohibited during inspections.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814257</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Anyone">
  <data key="d0">Anyone</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3180421cdd22a4773c6db6e08f304f90</data>
  <data key="d2">It is prohibited for anyone to hinder or obstruct Inspectors from performing their duties.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814258</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Administrative Penalties">
  <data key="d0">Administrative Penalties</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Administrative penalties are sanctions imposed by inspectors for minor violations of regulations, including warnings, orders to correct, and fines.&lt;SEP&gt;Sanctions imposed by the committee on violators as defined in Article Eighty-Eight.&lt;SEP&gt;Administrative Penalties are the collective sanctions imposed on economic operators for violating the system and regulations, as detailed in Article Seventy-Eight.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Minor Violations">
  <data key="d0">Minor Violations</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Minor violations are infractions defined by the regulation that warrant administrative penalties rather than more severe legal actions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814266</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="System">
  <data key="d0">System</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The System refers to the overarching legal framework that provides the basis for the regulation and the limits of penalties.&lt;SEP&gt;The System refers to the legal framework or regulations within which quality requirements and procedures are defined.&lt;SEP&gt;The System refers to the overarching legal framework whose publication date triggers the deadline for issuing the regulation.&lt;SEP&gt;The System refers to the overarching regulatory framework whose provisions are monitored and enforced by the Committee.&lt;SEP&gt;The System refers to the regulatory framework under which the administrative decision was issued.&lt;SEP&gt;The System refers to the overarching legal framework or code in which Article Twenty-Four is embedded.&lt;SEP&gt;The System refers to the regulation or legal framework whose effectiveness is governed by Article Twenty-Six.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-53d255606873f798c277f71c669581e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdd31cd82935851ed60fa97049b2dc09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e5edf0ea88592648169855ce547cfd5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4356d14be0458851058bcbfa4dd8eff9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1cdab301d132fa946f551f1fb83be2d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814646</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Warning">
  <data key="d0">Warning</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A warning is an administrative penalty issued to an economic operator upon detection of a minor violation.&lt;SEP&gt;A mild penalty issued to individuals who violate the system or regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5661f438c3dca334dc944b7a2eeeb87</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814603</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Order To Correct">
  <data key="d0">Order To Correct</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">An order to compel correction requires the economic operator to fix the violation within a specified timeframe in accordance with the law.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814267</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Fine">
  <data key="d0">Fine</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A fine is a monetary penalty not exceeding five thousand riyals imposed on the economic operator.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814267</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Five Thousand Riyals">
  <data key="d0">Five Thousand Riyals</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Five thousand riyals represents the maximum limit for administrative fines imposed for minor violations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814267</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 61">
  <data key="d0">Article 61</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 61 is the specific legal provision in the text that defines administrative penalties and their application.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1c88be299a43d67d9b9fc0d255ce74ea</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814267</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Sixty-Two">
  <data key="d0">Article Sixty-Two</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Sixty-Two is a legal provision concerning the Right to Object, establishing procedures for notifying operators of penalties and allowing them to appeal administrative decisions.&lt;SEP&gt;The legal article governing the submission of objections to the committee.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4761261f928e9e2a04c5cf880b36af44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Administrative Penalty Notice">
  <data key="d0">Administrative Penalty Notice</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Administrative Penalty Notice is a document that must clearly state the recipient's right to object and the procedures for doing so.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4761261f928e9e2a04c5cf880b36af44</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814272</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Committee">
  <data key="d0">Committee</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Committee is a body formed under Article Seventy-Five tasked with adjudicating objections within fifteen days.&lt;SEP&gt;The Committee referred to in Article Nineteen, Paragraph 1, responsible for adjudicating violations referred to it by the Minister.&lt;SEP&gt;The Committee investigates violations of regulations or bylaws and imposes penalties as outlined in Article Eighteen.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4761261f928e9e2a04c5cf880b36af44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-db15b26408bc87ab744a17b5b0ea6317&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdd31cd82935851ed60fa97049b2dc09</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814610</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Seventy-Five">
  <data key="d0">Article Seventy-Five</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Seventy-Five is the legal provision under which the Committee responsible for handling objections was formed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4761261f928e9e2a04c5cf880b36af44</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814273</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Competent Court">
  <data key="d0">Competent Court</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Competent Court is the judicial authority before which an objection to the Committee's decision may be filed.&lt;SEP&gt;The Competent Court is the judicial body authorized to hear cases, issue temporary orders, and render judgments regarding non-compliant practices.&lt;SEP&gt;The Competent Court is the judicial body responsible for examining and adjudicating disputes arising between consumers and economic operators.&lt;SEP&gt;The Competent Court is the judicial body where decisions regarding administrative penalties can be appealed.&lt;SEP&gt;The judicial body authorized to hear lawsuits arising from Article Ninety-Seven and impose sanctions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-4761261f928e9e2a04c5cf880b36af44&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e40f0555a179abb24172277f52bec711&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0f17c98aec4af855d06847e8dc54f39d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814439</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Interested Party">
  <data key="d0">Interested Party</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">An Interested Party has a stake in the matter and has the right to file lawsuits before competent courts regarding non-compliant practices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Chambers of Commerce">
  <data key="d0">Chambers of Commerce</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Chambers of Commerce are organizations with the legal right to file lawsuits in competent courts against non-compliant practices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Employers' Associations">
  <data key="d0">Employers' Associations</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Employers' Associations represent economic employers and can file lawsuits to address practices contrary to regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Non-Compliant Practices">
  <data key="d0">Non-Compliant Practices</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Non-Compliant Practices refer to business activities that violate regulations or standards, serving as the subject of legal injunctions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Compensation For Consumers">
  <data key="d0">Compensation For Consumers</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Compensation for Consumers refers to the financial redress awarded to consumers for damages and costs arising from non-compliant practices.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Corrosive Judgment">
  <data key="d0">Corrosive Judgment</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Corrosive Judgment (or Correctional Statement) is a public disclosure required by court order to correct misleading information related to the violation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Sixty-Three">
  <data key="d0">Article Sixty-Three</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Sixty-Three is the legal provision governing lawsuits to prevent non-compliant practices, outlining who can file suits and what judgments may include.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Temporary Order">
  <data key="d0">Temporary Order</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">A Temporary Order is a judicial measure issued by the competent court to stop or prevent non-compliant practices immediately.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Individual Consumer">
  <data key="d0">Individual Consumer</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">An Individual Consumer is a victim of non-compliant practices whose actual loss does not need to be proven by the plaintiff for representation purposes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814282</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Plaintiff">
  <data key="d0">Plaintiff</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b6a6d5fd04ff86c2506f73df9e65d57b</data>
  <data key="d2">The plaintiff is exempt from proving that each individual consumer suffered actual loss or damage.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814283</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 64">
  <data key="d0">Article 64</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 64 is a regulatory provision regarding the delegation of market surveillance activities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Market Surveillance Activities">
  <data key="d0">Market Surveillance Activities</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Market surveillance activities refer to the monitoring and enforcement actions conducted by competent authorities.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Concerned Parties">
  <data key="d0">Concerned Parties</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Concerned parties are entities to whom market surveillance activities may be delegated by the Competent Authority.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Private Sector">
  <data key="d0">Private Sector</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Private Sector is eligible to perform specific market surveillance activities under defined regulations, excluding punitive powers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Warnings">
  <data key="d0">Warnings</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Warnings are formal notifications issued as part of corrective measures, which cannot be delegated to the private sector.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Sanctions">
  <data key="d0">Sanctions</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Sanctions are penalties imposed for violations, which remain the exclusive authority of the Competent Authority.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="System And Bylaws">
  <data key="d0">System And Bylaws</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">System regulations and bylaws form the legal framework that governs market surveillance, with bylaws specifically setting controls for private sector involvement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-41f86c946795eb4b1b8e1172b283f83c</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814291</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Sixty-Five">
  <data key="d0">Article Sixty-Five</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Sixty-Five is a legal provision concerning the removal of harm from consumers and establishing their rights against economic operators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2e9d4353bb95f7bca809f541cd54320</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814300</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Harm">
  <data key="d0">Harm</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Harm refers to the damage or detriment suffered by a consumer as a result of the economic operator's failure to respect their rights or violation of regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2e9d4353bb95f7bca809f541cd54320</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814300</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Legal Violations">
  <data key="d0">Legal Violations</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Legal Violations refer to acts by the economic operator that contravene the system or regulations, potentially causing harm to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2e9d4353bb95f7bca809f541cd54320</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814300</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Replacement">
  <data key="d0">Product Replacement</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Product Replacement is a remedy where the consumer can request the exchange of the defective or problematic product.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2e9d4353bb95f7bca809f541cd54320</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814300</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Price Reduction">
  <data key="d0">Price Reduction</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Price Reduction is a financial remedy allowing the consumer to pay a lower price for the product affected by the violation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2e9d4353bb95f7bca809f541cd54320</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814300</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Damage Compensation">
  <data key="d0">Damage Compensation</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Damage Compensation is the monetary reparation owed to the consumer for the harm they have suffered.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2e9d4353bb95f7bca809f541cd54320</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814300</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Penalties And Punishments">
  <data key="d0">Penalties And Punishments</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Penalties And Punishments are additional sanctions imposed on the economic operator under the system, distinct from civil compensation to the consumer.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e2e9d4353bb95f7bca809f541cd54320</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814300</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Sixty-Six">
  <data key="d0">Article Sixty-Six</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Sixty-Six is a legal provision titled "Minor Claims" that defines the jurisdiction and procedure for handling small disputes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e40f0555a179abb24172277f52bec711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814310</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Minor Claims">
  <data key="d0">Minor Claims</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Minor Claims refer to small-value disputes or litigation matters that are eligible for simplified and expedited legal procedures.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e40f0555a179abb24172277f52bec711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814310</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Simplified Procedures">
  <data key="d0">Simplified Procedures</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Simplified Procedures are the specific legal mechanisms applied by the court to ensure rapid examination and resolution of minor claims.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e40f0555a179abb24172277f52bec711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814310</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Relevant Regulations">
  <data key="d0">Relevant Regulations</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Relevant Regulations are the existing legal frameworks that define the scope and application of the simplified procedures for minor claims.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e40f0555a179abb24172277f52bec711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814310</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Alternative Means For Dispute Resolution">
  <data key="d0">Alternative Means For Dispute Resolution</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Alternative Means For Dispute Resolution refers to fair, effective, and neutral methods available for settling conflicts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b54adc716da8570bddd8c2bd41899a6f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814321</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Unified Network">
  <data key="d0">Unified Network</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Unified Network is a structured system established among alternative dispute resolution providers and electronic platforms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b54adc716da8570bddd8c2bd41899a6f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814321</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dispute Resolution Providers">
  <data key="d0">Dispute Resolution Providers</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Dispute Resolution Providers are entities offering alternative means for resolving consumer-economic operator conflicts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b54adc716da8570bddd8c2bd41899a6f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814321</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 67">
  <data key="d0">Article 67</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 67 is the specific legal provision titled "Alternative Means for Dispute Resolution" that establishes the framework for consumer dispute resolution.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-b54adc716da8570bddd8c2bd41899a6f</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814321</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Sixty-Eight">
  <data key="d0">Article Sixty-Eight</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Sixty-Eight is a legal provision concerning the supervision of alternative dispute resolution providers and electronic platforms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814334</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Ministry of Justice">
  <data key="d0">Ministry of Justice</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Ministry of Justice collaborates with the Competent Authority in supervising alternative dispute resolution providers and electronic platforms.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ministry of Justice collaborates with the Competent Authority to establish the regulatory framework for alternative dispute resolution services.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60f77fe5478de7b3d8b2672afe5ee95d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814350</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Alternative Dispute Resolution Providers">
  <data key="d0">Alternative Dispute Resolution Providers</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">These are entities providing alternative means for resolving disputes between consumers and economic operators, subject to supervision.&lt;SEP&gt;Entities providing alternative dispute resolution services, required to ensure arbitrators and experts are experienced, independent, and neutral.&lt;SEP&gt;These are entities providing means for resolving disputes outside of traditional courts, subject to specific establishment and operational regulations.&lt;SEP&gt;Entities responsible for providing alternative means of dispute resolution, subject to transparency and reporting obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d8a453039317884766c4bfb4e705a9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60f77fe5478de7b3d8b2672afe5ee95d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8eba08bab139116de9ee95fe214a7f7e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814366</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Platforms For Dispute Resolution">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Platforms For Dispute Resolution</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Electronic platforms used for settling disputes between consumers and economic operators, which require operational reports and quality guidelines.&lt;SEP&gt;Digital platforms facilitating dispute resolution, subject to requirements for effective, fair, and transparent procedures.&lt;SEP&gt;Digital platforms facilitating dispute resolution, required to maintain transparency and submit activity reports.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d8a453039317884766c4bfb4e705a9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8eba08bab139116de9ee95fe214a7f7e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814366</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Committee For Alternative Means And Electronic Platforms">
  <data key="d0">Committee For Alternative Means And Electronic Platforms</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">This committee is formed by the Competent Authority to manage tasks related to alternative dispute resolution and electronic platforms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814334</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quality Guidelines">
  <data key="d0">Quality Guidelines</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Guidelines issued to specify quality requirements and assurance procedures for dispute resolution processes as defined in the system.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814334</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Training Requirements">
  <data key="d0">Training Requirements</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Requirements determining the necessary training for officials regarding procedures for settling disputes via alternative means and electronic platforms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814334</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Operational Reports">
  <data key="d0">Operational Reports</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Reports collected from dispute resolution providers and platforms, which are analyzed and summarized for public disclosure.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814334</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="General Public">
  <data key="d0">General Public</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d72a2ff68ca9639d25fac0d200e648dd</data>
  <data key="d2">Summaries of operational reports are made available to the general public.</data>
  <data key="d1">UNKNOWN</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814335</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Arbitrators">
  <data key="d0">Arbitrators</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Specialists involved in dispute resolution who must possess experience, independence, and neutrality.&lt;SEP&gt;Arbitrators are individuals involved in dispute resolution, subject to specific requirements and conditions set by the regulatory body.&lt;SEP&gt;Individuals appointed to resolve disputes through arbitration, whose names and appointment methods must be disclosed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5d8a453039317884766c4bfb4e705a9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60f77fe5478de7b3d8b2672afe5ee95d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8eba08bab139116de9ee95fe214a7f7e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814366</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Mediators">
  <data key="d0">Mediators</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Specialists involved in dispute resolution who must possess experience, independence, and neutrality.&lt;SEP&gt;Mediators are individuals who assist in resolving disputes, regulated under the same requirements as arbitrators and experts.&lt;SEP&gt;Individuals facilitating negotiation between parties in a dispute, whose names and appointment methods must be disclosed.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5d8a453039317884766c4bfb4e705a9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60f77fe5478de7b3d8b2672afe5ee95d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8eba08bab139116de9ee95fe214a7f7e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814366</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Experts">
  <data key="d0">Experts</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Specialists assisting in dispute resolution who must possess experience, independence, and neutrality.&lt;SEP&gt;Experts provide specialized knowledge in dispute resolution processes, governed by specific qualifications and obligations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5d8a453039317884766c4bfb4e705a9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-60f77fe5478de7b3d8b2672afe5ee95d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814351</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Dispute Resolution Procedures">
  <data key="d0">Dispute Resolution Procedures</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Processes for resolving disputes via alternative means and electronic platforms, which must be effective, fair, independent, transparent, and orderly.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-5d8a453039317884766c4bfb4e705a9a</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
