  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Defined Compensation">
  <data key="d0">Defined Compensation</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The type and value of compensation determined during the dispute resolution process.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8eba08bab139116de9ee95fe214a7f7e</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814367</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Seventy-Two">
  <data key="d0">Article Seventy-Two</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Seventy-Two is a legal provision focused on quality assurance, establishing rules for maintaining the efficiency of alternative dispute resolution providers and electronic platforms.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-396aa1e5ed51d610f5f6e15aaf6ec6b6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814372</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Quality Assurance">
  <data key="d0">Quality Assurance</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Quality Assurance refers to the mechanisms and procedures defined in Article Seventy-Two to ensure standards are met within the dispute resolution network.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-396aa1e5ed51d610f5f6e15aaf6ec6b6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814372</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Alternative Dispute Resolution Providers Network">
  <data key="d0">Alternative Dispute Resolution Providers Network</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The network consists of providers offering alternative dispute resolution services, whose efficiency must be maintained through specific safeguards.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-396aa1e5ed51d610f5f6e15aaf6ec6b6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814372</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Dispute Settlement Platforms">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Dispute Settlement Platforms</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">These are digital platforms used for settling disputes, subject to regulations ensuring their operational efficiency and quality.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-396aa1e5ed51d610f5f6e15aaf6ec6b6</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814372</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Seventy-Three">
  <data key="d0">Article Seventy-Three</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Seventy-Three is a legal provision governing collective lawsuits and the rights of consumer associations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-da4dec7a272932b152bbbcd68d8fab88</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814379</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Courts">
  <data key="d0">Courts</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Courts are the judicial bodies where Consumer Associations can file lawsuits regarding collective consumer rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-da4dec7a272932b152bbbcd68d8fab88</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814379</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Collective Lawsuits">
  <data key="d0">Collective Lawsuits</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Collective Lawsuits are legal actions filed by or joined by Consumer Associations to address violations against consumer rights.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-da4dec7a272932b152bbbcd68d8fab88</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814379</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Individual Consumers">
  <data key="d0">Individual Consumers</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Individual Consumers are persons who retain the right to claim their own rights separately or collectively, as preserved by Article Seventy-Three.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-da4dec7a272932b152bbbcd68d8fab88</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814379</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Seventy-Four">
  <data key="d0">Article Seventy-Four</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Seventy-Four is a legal provision defining the jurisdiction of courts regarding consumer disputes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec93773600936293052d86178a78f903</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814385</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Specialized Court">
  <data key="d0">Specialized Court</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Specialized Court is the judicial body competent to hear cases arising from consumer disputes and remote contracts.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec93773600936293052d86178a78f903</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814385</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Disputes">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Disputes</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer Disputes refer to conflicts between consumers and businesses that are subject to judicial review.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec93773600936293052d86178a78f903</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814385</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Domicile">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Domicile</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Consumer Domicile refers to the residence or place of stay of a consumer, which determines the territorial jurisdiction of the court.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec93773600936293052d86178a78f903</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814385</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Court Competence">
  <data key="d0">Court Competence</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Court Competence is the legal authority of a specific court to hear and decide cases, defined by Article Seventy-Four.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ec93773600936293052d86178a78f903</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814385</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Review Committee For Violations">
  <data key="d0">Review Committee For Violations</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A committee established by the competent authority's decision to examine violations of system and regulation provisions, consisting of at least three members including at least one permanent advisor.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="System And Regulation Provisions">
  <data key="d0">System And Regulation Provisions</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The legal framework and rules whose violation is subject to review and penalty by the committee.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Objections Under Article Sixty-Two">
  <data key="d0">Objections Under Article Sixty-Two</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Formal appeals or objections submitted to the committee for consideration under specific legal provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Specific Economic Sectors">
  <data key="d0">Specific Economic Sectors</data>
  <data key="d1">category</data>
  <data key="d2">Economic sectors targeted for specialized committees to handle violations relevant to their specific industries.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Permanent Advisor">
  <data key="d0">Permanent Advisor</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">A permanent advisor is a required member of the Review Committee For Violations, ensuring at least one such advisor is present among the members.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Seventy-Seven">
  <data key="d0">Article Seventy-Seven</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The legal article specifying the corrective measures that the committee may adopt.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Eighty-Eight">
  <data key="d0">Article Eighty-Eight</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The legal article defining the administrative penalties that the committee may impose on violators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a77f891792f59dafbde31f28e906bdf0</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814393</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Seventy-Six">
  <data key="d0">Article Seventy-Six</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Seventy-Six is a legal provision outlining the criteria for determining penalties imposed by a committee.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814404</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="The Committee">
  <data key="d0">The Committee</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Committee is the authority responsible for imposing penalties based on specific criteria outlined in Article Seventy-Six.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814404</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Violation Severity">
  <data key="d0">Violation Severity</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Violation severity refers to the gravity or seriousness of an infraction, which influences penalty determination.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdd31cd82935851ed60fa97049b2dc09</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814404</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Recurrence">
  <data key="d0">Recurrence</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Recurrence refers to the frequency or repetition of violations, considered when setting penalties.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814404</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Circumstances">
  <data key="d0">Circumstances</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Circumstances refer to the context and conditions surrounding the violation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814404</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consequences">
  <data key="d0">Consequences</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Consequences refer to the effects or outcomes resulting from the violation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814404</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Damage">
  <data key="d0">Damage</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Damage refers to the harm or loss incurred as a result of the violation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
