<node id="Activity Volume">
  <data key="d0">Activity Volume</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Activity volume refers to the scale or size of the violator's operations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814404</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Duration Of Activity">
  <data key="d0">Duration Of Activity</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Duration of activity refers to the length of time the violator engaged in the relevant activity.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-72929fe75d8e8a52b412bbb808e64665</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814404</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Committee For Examining Violations">
  <data key="d0">Committee For Examining Violations</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Committee for Examining Violations is the regulatory body authorized to issue warnings, impose corrective measures, and make decisions regarding regulatory violations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Consumer Protection System And Regulation">
  <data key="d0">Consumer Protection System And Regulation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The Consumer Protection System And Regulation is the legal framework containing Article 77 that defines corrective measures for violations by economic operators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Electronic Platform">
  <data key="d0">Electronic Platform</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">An electronic platform is a digital interface whose content, access, or operation may be restricted or suspended as a corrective measure for violations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Domain Name Registrars">
  <data key="d0">Domain Name Registrars</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Domain name registrars are entities ordered to delete domain names and allow relevant parties to register them as part of corrective enforcement.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Hosting Service Providers">
  <data key="d0">Hosting Service Providers</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Hosting service providers are required to restrict, block, or shut down access to electronic platforms hosting violating content upon committee order.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Judicial Decision">
  <data key="d0">Judicial Decision</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">A judicial decision refers to a court ruling that can halt the execution of the Committee's corrective measures if deemed appropriate.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article 77">
  <data key="d0">Article 77</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Article 77 is the specific section of the regulation titled "Corrective Measures" that outlines the Committee's powers and the types of penalties for violations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Contract Or Terms">
  <data key="d0">Contract Or Terms</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Contracts or terms related to the violation may be suspended until the issue is resolved.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Confiscated Products">
  <data key="d0">Confiscated Products</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Products involved in violations are detained by authorities pending investigation or judicial ruling.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-51ea5244ed2d72532c1d4e4a8c7c8711</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814415</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Seventy-Eight">
  <data key="d0">Article Seventy-Eight</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Seventy-Eight is a legal provision detailing administrative penalties for economic operators who violate the system and regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="The System">
  <data key="d0">The System</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The System refers to the overarching regulatory framework that defines obligations for economic operators.&lt;SEP&gt;The system refers to the regulatory framework or legal code whose provisions are being defined in Article Two.&lt;SEP&gt;The System refers to a legislative framework or law that has been officially published.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b912e56726cb9e0d5237d61584a5fa6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3323a5605fc02cf6b08e6daf15866451</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814642</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Administrative Warning">
  <data key="d0">Administrative Warning</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">An Administrative Warning is a penalty issued to an Economic Operator for violating the System or Regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Seizure">
  <data key="d0">Product Seizure</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Product Seizure involves confiscating the product that was the subject of the violation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Service Prohibition">
  <data key="d0">Service Prohibition</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Service Prohibition bans the provision of a service, either temporarily or permanently, due to violations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Product Recall">
  <data key="d0">Product Recall</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Product Recall requires the retrieval of non-compliant products according to specified regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Monetary Fine">
  <data key="d0">Monetary Fine</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">A Monetary Fine is a financial penalty not exceeding 100,000 Riyals imposed on violators.&lt;SEP&gt;A financial penalty capped at one million riyals imposed on violators.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5661f438c3dca334dc944b7a2eeeb87</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814603</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Activity Suspension">
  <data key="d0">Activity Suspension</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Activity Suspension halts business operations, partially or fully, for up to 90 days, including closing physical locations and blocking websites.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Local Newspapers">
  <data key="d0">Local Newspapers</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">Local Newspapers are publications in the offender's place of residence used for publishing penalty rulings.&lt;SEP&gt;Local newspapers are publications issued in the violator's place of residence, used as a medium for publishing penalty decisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85d489500ac41fa5ad12a8c9462979b4</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك&lt;SEP&gt;نظام_التجارة_الإلكترونية</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814626</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Appropriate Means">
  <data key="d0">Appropriate Means</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">Appropriate Means refer to alternative communication channels designated by competent authorities for publishing penalty rulings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-c473b635efc04ff40f299b6d7f6fc2db</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814426</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Article Ninety-Seven">
  <data key="d0">Article Ninety-Seven</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Article Ninety-Seven is a legal provision detailing criminal penalties, specifically fines and jurisdictional responsibilities for various violations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0f17c98aec4af855d06847e8dc54f39d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814438</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Three Million Riyals">
  <data key="d0">Three Million Riyals</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The maximum fine amount imposed under Article Ninety-Seven is three million riyals.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-0f17c98aec4af855d06847e8dc54f39d</data>
  <data key="d4">مشروع_نظام_حماية_المستهلك</data>
  <data key="d5">1776814438</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
