<edge source="Consumer" target="Product">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Products are offered to Consumers.&lt;SEP&gt;The Consumer must care for the Product and limit its use to verifying compliance with the Systematic Warranty as per Article 49.&lt;SEP&gt;The Consumer is obligated to return the Product to the Economic Operator within seven days of termination notification.&lt;SEP&gt;The Consumer must take care of the Product and limit its use to what is necessary to verify compliance with the statutory warranty in Article 49.&lt;SEP&gt;The Consumer is obligated to return the Product to the Economic Operator or their representative within seven days of contract termination.</data>
