</edge>
<edge source="Consumer" target="Alternative Means For Dispute Resolution">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Consumers have the right to use alternative means for dispute resolution to settle conflicts.&lt;SEP&gt;Consumers have the right to use Alternative Means For Dispute Resolution to settle conflicts with economic operators, as established in Article 67.</data>
  <data key="d9">access,legal right</data>
