<edge source="Economic Operator" target="Carrier">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">If the Economic Operator recommends the Carrier, the Consumer does not bear liability for the Product's loss, protecting the Operator from indirect risk via Consumer choice.</data>
