</edge>
<edge source="Economic Operator" target="Article Forty-Six">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Article Forty-Six establishes the legal requirement for the Economic Operator to ensure compliance.&lt;SEP&gt;Article Forty-Six provides the specific requirements that define whether a product or service is compliant.</data>
  <data key="d9">compliance benchmark,legal obligation,regulation,requirement reference</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-c6572d1610f6bb7f6ec41fc6f8eb934f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6d5f73112067d3017eacad446fe05c6c</data>
