</edge>
<edge source="Article Thirty-Three: Liability for Loss" target="Delivery">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The occurrence of Delivery is the primary legal trigger that determines whether the Economic Operator or Consumer bears the liability for the Product's loss.</data>
  <data key="d9">legal trigger,risk transfer</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-4a056e5bd9daa08695b5a665b53f6d3b</data>
