</edge>
<edge source="المادة العشرون" target="Diwan Al-Muzalim Litigation System">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Article Twenty mandates that appeals be filed according to the rules of the Diwan Al-Muzalim Litigation System.</data>
